Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Burayi/mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, wiyongereye cyane hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza bihuriyeho, byemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byose nubwo ibihe bitandukanye.
Ukurikije ubunararibonye bw'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima by'indwara zikomeye bigomba kongera imyiteguro ku mubare wihuta w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu buvuzi bw'indwara z'indwara z'indwara zikomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari urukurikirane rw'abantu bagaragaweho indwara ya Pneumonia itera indwara z'amasoro zitazwi, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko hari coronavirus nshya ifite ubwandu bw'indwara, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kubera ko iyi ndwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, yahawe izina rya Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso byerekana ko 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara zidakomeye, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa na Pneumonia cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri bo bakize.
Mu bantu 14%, COVID-19 ifata imiterere y'uburwayi bukomeye cyane, bigatuma umuntu ajya mu bitaro, mu gihe mu bantu 6%, uburwayi bukomeye cyane, bukenera ubuvuzi bwimbitse.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ibyago bya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) tugereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'abanduye mu Butaliyani hagati ya tariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu turere twinshi, kandi imibare y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bihugu byose by'isi ubu irakurikirana uko ibintu byifashe muri iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ibaruwa yo ku wa 5 Werurwe yo muri EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al, yatangaje ko hari umuntu wa mbere w'i Burayi wanduye COVID-19 nk'uko byasobanuwe na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020, u Bufaransa bwatangaje ko bwabonye abanduye batatu ba mbere bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (UK) byamaze kugaragaza ko byanduye COVID-19, aho ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 no kuri uwo munsi hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 39,768 n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 17,750 n'abantu 1,441.
