Muri rusange, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma itangira kwiyongera ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi byiganjemo ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abanduye muri Italy ariko kandi n'ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA na UK na byo byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye (Igitabo cy'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Byongeye kandi, byerekana ko hari ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutangazwa umubare ungana n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 mbere ya saa munani za mu gitondo ku ya 15 Werurwe.
