Imiterere y'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 byerekanye ko icyorezo kirimo kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Byongeye kandi, kubera ko ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu bihe bitandukanye, intera iri hagati y'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange by'igihugu n'ubushobozi bwo gusobanura ubwandu butandukanye hagati y'ibihugu, ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi, birakenewe ko asuzumwa kugirango hamenyekane COVID-19, harimo no gupima.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byatewe n'icyorezo basobanuye ko 10% by'abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru agaragaza ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe byo muri ibyo bice byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe ubu aboneka ku barwayi 6% na 1% ku rwego rwa EU/EEA (nta makuru agaragara).
Ariko kandi, bagomba gukusanya amakuru y'ubugenzuzi buriho mu buryo buhuza, bwibanze ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU n'ibyo mu bitaro byagutse, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29.2 ku baturage 100,000, naho muri Porutugali hari ibitanda 4.2.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu byinshi bifite ibikoresho bike cyangwa byinshi kuruta u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ubuvuzi bworoheje ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Umubare munini w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ni ibipimo byerekana ko ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima buhagaze neza, bufite ibyago > 90% byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo kwa muganga, nk'uko byatanzwe mu byiciro bya gatandatu bya ECDC Rapid Risk Assessment of COVID-19.
