Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abashinzwe ubuzima batanga raporo z'ubwandu, bagaragaza ko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warashyizwe mu kato burundu, kandi ingendo zose z'abantu ku isi zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bamaze kumenyekana, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, ryatekerejweho ko ari ahantu hatangiriye ubwandu buturutse ku matungo atazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku buzima ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yasohokaga, iki cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo cya 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse, imiterere n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo biracyari mu rujijo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866, harimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19 ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, butanga ishusho iheruka y'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura abantu b'imyaka yose ariko yibasira cyane cyane abantu bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka 50 y'amavuko, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi cyane (0.27/1,00,000) kurusha abagore (0.31/1,00,000).
