Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi byateza COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (>60) na Pneumonia ikaze.
CoV ni umuryango muto wa virusi nini kandi zihuze, zirimo insinga imwe ya RNA y'ubushake.
Zishobora kugabanywamo imiterere ine, ari yo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, muri zo alpha- na beta CoV bizwi ko zangiza abantu.
Iyi glycoprotein y'isura (S) ifata ku byuma byayo by'indwara ya Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) na Dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), ku buryo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hanyuma igatera uruhu guhinduka.
Igitsina cy'agakoko giteye virusi RNA gisohoka mu mwuka; nyuma yo gukora kopi ya virusi, RNA ya genomic ihinduka iseru y'ibinure birimo glycoproteins n'indwara ya nucleocapsid, nyuma bigasohoka mu mubiri bigasohoka mu mubiri.
Urukurikirane rwa mbere rwa genomic rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwanditswe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
