SARS-CoV-2 ifite byinshi ihuriyeho na MERS-CoV kurusha SARS-CoV.
Binyuze mu gukoresha mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike yo gutwara, udukoko twa SARS-CoV-2 twabonetse mu bice byoroheje cyane by'urwungano rw'umuhogo w'umuntu.
Abantu ACE2 yagaragaye ko ari receptor ya SARS-CoV-2 ndetse na SARS-CoV.
Icyakora, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2 y'umuntu mu buryo budafite imbaraga nyinshi kurusha poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bituma SARS-CoV-2 idatera indwara zikomeye cyane nk'iza SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ntoya, isimburwa na orf3b, na poroteyine y'umwimerere isimburwa na orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite orf3b ishobora kugira uruhare mu ndwara zandura kandi ikabuza IFNß kugaragaza; ariko, orf8 nta gice cy'ingenzi kizwi cyangwa intego igaragara.
