Umuryango n'umuyoboro
Bizwi ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byombi byakomotse ku birura, kandi byandujwe n'abantu binyuze mu gupima ingurube n'ingamiya.
Iyo SARS-CoV-2 igereranyijwe mu mateka y'ibinyabuzima n'izindi virusi zandura, inyamaswa z'ibinyugunyugu ni zo zigize SARS-CoV-2 kuko virusi nshya ihuriyeho na 96% n'izindi virusi zandura zimeze nka SARS, nk'izitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko ntibiramenyekana neza uburyo bw'ibanze bw'abanduye bwafashije virusi kurenga inzitizi y'ubwoko mu kwanduza abantu, kandi inzira y'ubwandu iracyari hanze.
Ji, et al., batanga igitekerezo cy'uko inzoka zigomba kuba ari zo zigize uruhu rw'inyamaswa kugira ngo zigere ku bantu, aho byashoboka ko hari ihurizo ry'igitsina hagati ya poroteyine S.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bwagaragaje ko injangwe zirya ibishyimbo, zikunda gukoresha imiti gakondo mu Bushinwa, zishobora kuba ari zo nyamaswa z'ibanze zanduza SARS-CoV-2, aho COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu binyabuzima by'ibishyimbo, bifitaniye isano rya 99% mu miterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Ariko kandi, intera iri hagati ya 1% hagati ya genome ebyiri iracyari ndende, bityo hagitegerejwe ibimenyetso bifatika kugira ngo hagere ku mwanzuro uhamye (Igishushanyo cya 33).
Imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 ntiharamenyekana neza.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe, ndetse no mu gihe cy'iminsi 5 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe bwa 40-50% na 20°C.
SARS-CoV-2 na yo ifite ubwo bushobozi.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 idashobora kwihanganira imirasire y'umuriro wa ultraviolet n'ubushyuhe bwa 56°C nyuma y'iminota 30, Ether, 75% ya éthanol, umuti wica mikorobe urimo chlorine, acide paracéttique, chloroforme na chlorhexidine, uretse ibindi bikoresho bya medaméldéthane, bishobora kuyirwanya mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza.
Ubusanzwe abantu bose ntibashobora guhangana na SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe ku bijyanye n'igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Bityo rero, dushobora kwerekeza gusa ku bushakashatsi ku zindi CoVs, cyane cyane: SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo cya 4).
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi igeze ku nyamaswa, imenyerezwa na receptor zo kumenya imiterere (PRR), zirimo C-type lectin-like receptors, Toll-like receptors (TLR), NOD-like receptors (NLR) na RIG-like receptors (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho kugaragaza ibintu by'ubukana, gukura kwa dendritic n'uburyo bwa mbere bwo guhungabanya (INN), bigatuma virusi itagera ku bandi kandi ikongera umuvuduko wa fagositosis y'imyanya ndangagitsina y'indwara.
Icyakora, poroteyine N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi guhangana n'igisubizo cy'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Bidatinze, abashinzwe kurwanya indwara bahise batangira kurwana na virusi.
T lymphocytes, hamwe na CD4+ na CD8+ T cells, igira uruhare runini mu kurinda.
CD4+ T zashishikariza B cells gukora antibodies zihariye kuri virusi, naho CD8+ T zigasenya virusi zigakomeretsa.
Kugira ngo intanga ngabo zifashe intanga ngabo, intanga ngabo zitanga cytokines z'ubuhumekero.
Icyakora, COVID T ishobora kubuza ingirabuzimafatizo gukora binyuze mu gutuma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zangiza.
Igisirikare cy'umubiri gisanzwe gikorana n'ibindi bice by'umubiri n'udufaranga nka C3A na C5A na byo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bakuwe mu barwayi bakize, bashoboye guhashya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, uburyo bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara butuma habaho imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi zitagira ingufu zishobora kwangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu bihe bibi cyane, zishobora kwangiza ingingo zitandukanye ndetse no gutuma umuntu apfa.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 itangirira mu itsinda, ishobora kuba yiganje cyane mu bantu bakuze bafite uburwayi bw'indwara ifata imyanya ndangagitsina, ndetse no mu bagore batwite.
Abantu bafite izindi ndwara cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budafite imbaraga, bashobora kwandura kurusha abandi.
Igihe cyo kubyaza umusaruro cya SARS-CoV-2 kigereranywa n'iminsi 1-14 mu gihe abenshi mu barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 baba bamaze iminsi iri hagati ya 3 na 7 nk'uko byagenze mu gihe cy'abantu 425 ba mbere bagaragaye muri Wuhan.
Ariko, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 1,099 bwerekanye ko igihe cyo kuvura cyari iminsi 3 kandi ko cyari hagati y'iminsi 0 na 24.
Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, ubushakashatsi buherutse cyane bwerekanye ko igihe cyo kubyaza umusaruro mu baturage 8,866 cy'ibyago cyari iminsi 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Ni ngombwa cyane ku bayobozi b'ubuzima gushyira hamwe igihe cyiza cyo kwitarura abantu, hashingiwe ku gihe cyiza cyo kugabanya ubukana, kugira ngo abantu banduye ariko badafite ibimenyetso batanduza abandi.
Mu ngamba rusange, abantu bahuye cyangwa banduye virusi bakwiriye gushyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ese ni ngombwa ko umuntu amara iminsi 24 mu kato?
Ubushyuhe ni cyo kimenyetso cy'ibanze cya COVID-19, gishobora guherekezwa no kutagira ibimenyetso cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso nk'inkorora, kugira isesemi, guhinda umushyitsi, kugira isesemi, umutwe, kuribwa mu muhogo, impumuro mbi, kubabara mu gatuza, iseseme, kugira iseseme no gusubiranamo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bashobora kugira ikibazo cyo kutabona no/cyangwa hypoxemia nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe barwaye.
Mu bihe bikomeye, abarwayi bahita bagerwaho n'indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero, impiswi, acidosis yo mu mubiri n'uburwayi bw'amaraso.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero hamwe n'umuriro ukabije, bagomba gupimwa virusi kugira ngo bagaragazwe hakiri kare, byaba ari ukugaragaza udukoko tw'indwara z'ibihaha cyangwa se udukoko tw'ibihaha.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, bwagaragaje ko ibimenyetso byari 98% by'umuriro, 76% by'iseru ryumye, 55% by'indwara ya dyspnea na 3% by'iseru; 8% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Ubushakashatsi bushya bwakozwe ku bantu babiri bahuye n'indwara y'ibicurane mu muryango no ku bantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso, na bwo bwagaragaje ko abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibicurane.
Mu kugereranya, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bari bafite umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%) na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi.
Ariko kandi, 80% muri bo bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka, umubare munini cyane ugereranyije n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi MERS yari ifite ubukana burenze ubwa COVID-19.
Kuribwa cyane n'igifu (26%) no kuribwa mu muhogo (21%) na byo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, byagaragaye ko umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora yumye (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), impiswi (20-25%) no kuribwa mu muhogo (13-25%) ari byo bimenyetso by'ingenzi, kandi hafi 14% na 20% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye inkunga yo guhumeka.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, igihe imibare y'abanduye isi yose yari imaze kugera ku 66,576, umubare w'abapfa kubera COVID-19 wari ku kigero cya 2%.
Mu kugereranya, kugeza mu Gushyingo 2002, SARS yari ifite igipimo cy'urupfu kiri ku kigero cya 10% ku bantu 8,096 bamaze kwandura.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, igipimo cy'urupfu cyavuye ku byigwa byakozwe muri Kamena 2012 ku bantu 2494 banduye, kigera kuri 37%.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yari ifite RO iri hejuru ya 6.47 mu gihe 95% by'ibipimo by'icyizere (CI) byari hagati ya 5.71 na 7.23, mu gihe SARS-CoV yari ifite RO iri hagati ya 2 na 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV mu bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, igipimo cy'urupfu na RO, bigaragara mu mbonerahamwe 1.1.
Ibipimo byavuzwe haruguru bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ko ari zo ziteza ubwandu buke.
Ku bw'ibyo, kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 biragoye cyane kurusha kurwanya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Ubusanzwe gutangira muri rusange bitangirira mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu muhango umwe cyangwa mu bwato bumwe, nk'ubwato bw'urugendo.
Abarwayi bafite amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa ahandi hantu hari icyorezo, cyangwa bagiranye isano n'abantu banduye, cyangwa mu byumweru bibiri bishize icyorezo kitaraza.
Icyakora, byemejwe ko abantu bashobora kugira virusi nta bimenyetso mu gihe kirenze ibyumweru bibiri, kandi ko abarwayi bakize bavuye mu bitaro bashobora kongera gutwara virusi, bikaba byaratumye hagirwa inama yo kongera igihe cyo kwitarura.
Mu gihe cy'ibanze, abarwayi bafite ingirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso yera (cyane cyane za 'lymphocyte') mu rugero ruciriritse cyangwa ruri kugabanuka.
Urugero, abarwayi 1,099 ba COVID-19 basanganywe indwara ya lymphopenia ifite ingano y'utugingo tw'amaraso twera < 4×109/L harimo n'umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso < 1×109/L, kandi bagaragaweho kugira amineotransferase yo hejuru n'indwara ya viremia.
Hari abarwayi bagaragaje ko amaraso yabo yari afite ibipimo bya enzymes z'imitsi n'imitsi n'ibyitwa myoglobin, kandi abarwayi benshi bari bafite ibipimo bya poroteyine z'umusemburo wa C n'ibyitwa erythrocytes.
Mu barwayi barwaye cyane, ingano ya D-dimer mu maraso ituruka ku gusenyuka kwa fibrin yariyongereye, kandi umubare w'indwara z'amaraso wagabanutse cyane.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragayeho ibintu bidasanzwe mu mashusho y'igituza, byaranzwe n'ibice bibiri by'ibice by'ibihaha cyangwa ubukana bw'ibirahuri.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira uburwayi bw'ibihaha, ibikomere bikomeye by'ibihaha n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (ARDS).
Iyo ARDS ibayeho, irondaruhu ritagira ingufu, gukomera kw'amazi no guhinduka kw'umwijima w'ikirere bigira ingaruka ku mwuka.
Imikorere mibi ya Pneumocytes y'ubwoko bwa 1 n'ubw'ubwoko bwa 2 ituma uruhu rwayo rucika kandi rugatera imihangayiko, bigatuma imikorere y'ibihaha igabanuka kandi bigatuma ibyago byo kwandura byongera.
Bityo rero, ibisubizo bibi cyane bya radiyografi akenshi biba ari bimwe n'iby'indwara zikomeye cyane.
Igenzura rya mbere ry'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 ryo ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020 ryerekanye ko gusenya uduhimba tw'imyakura, imiterere y'urukuta rw'indwara n'igogorwa ry'uduhimba tw'imyakura n'utugingo tw'amasohoro tw'indwara zo mu nda mu maraso y'abarwayi bapfuye, bihuye n'uburwayi bw'indwara ziterwa n'indwara ya virusi na ARDS kandi bisa n'ibyabaye ku barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kumenya SARS-CoV-2 RNA binyuze mu buryo bwo gusubiza inyuma inyandiko za polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) byakoreshejwe nk'ingingo y'ingenzi mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera ko umubare munini w'abanduye indwara zidakira zateye imbere, ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020, mu Bushinwa hatangiye gukoreshwa ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi (bitagishingiye ku buryo bwa RT-PCR gusa) mu gusuzuma indwara.
Ibintu nk'ibyo byabayeho igihe SARS yagaragazwaga.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhuza amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi, ibizamini byo mu bitaro n'ibisubizo bya radiyoloji ni ingenzi kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo haboneke umuti ufatika.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha CRISPR-shingiye kuri SHERLOCK mu kumenya SARS-CoV-2, aho imyanda y'umwanda SARS-CoV-2 ya RNA ivurwa kuva kuri 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (amoko 10-100 kuri microliter y'ibikoresho) mu gihe cy'isaha imwe, hatagikenewe ibikoresho byinshi.
Byitezwe ko niba byemejwe mu bipimo by'ubuvuzi, ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ibyiyumvo n'ubworoherane.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye kuri CoV nshya, abaganga bashobora guha abarwayi ba COVID-19 ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi gusa, bagerageza uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere kuri CoVs zimwe na zimwe, nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hamwe n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).
Muri ubwo buryo bwo kuvura harimo imiti ya virusi, imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'uburyo bwo kuvura ubu n'ubushobozi bwo kwiyumvisha ibintu.
Si ibyo gusa ahubwo hari n'ibitekerezo byo gukoresha ingirabuzimafatizo z'abarwayi bakize mu kuvura.
Amashyirahamwe akora imiti arimo gukora cyane mu gukora antibody n'inkingo kuri virusi.
