Uretse udupfukamunwa, abashinzwe ubuzima basabwa kwambara imyenda y'ubwigunge ifatanye n'imyenda kugira ngo birinde guhura n'ubwandu.
Virusi ishobora no kwanduza abantu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; birashoboka ko virusi yageze mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye aremereye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abavura bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa indorerwamo mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Abaturage muri rusange bo mu bice byatewe cyangwa bishobora kwandura, barasabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha uko bisanzwe bakoresheje isabune yica udukoko, kuguma mu ngo zabo kugira ngo bishyire mu kato no kugabanya guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Abantu bakwiriye kugendera kure y'umurwayi nibura metero eshatu.
Ibi bikorwa byatangiye gufatwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje mu bantu nk'agakoko gashya, nk'uko byavuzwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, yagombaga kuba ari akayaga gakomeye mu Bushinwa kubera ko yari ifite ibyago byo kwandura SARS-CoV, nk'uko byatangajwe mu 2003 mu mateka.
Ariko, na mbere y'aho ku ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yabwiraga abantu ko virusi nshya idashobora kwanduza cyane kandi ko idashobora kuvuka cyane hagati y'abantu, kandi ko kwirinda no kugenzura iyi ndwara bitoroshye.
Ubu butumwa bwagabanyije cyane ubushishozi mu baturage cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari kigiye gutangira ibirori by'Ubunani, kandi Wuhan yari ibura umwanya ukomeye wo kugabanya icyorezo.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa gishobora kwigira ku masomo y'urujijo kandi kigakora impinduka zikomeye mu gihe kiri imbere.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba kugira amakenga (1) kurushaho kwitonda mu gihe bitangaza ku mugaragaro kuko ijambo ryose rivuzwe ku baturage rifite agaciro kandi rishobora guhindura imyumvire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kurushaho kumva no kwitabira amakuru adasanzwe mu mavuriro aho gutegereza raporo z'imikorere y'abaganga cyangwa abaforomo; (3) gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira icyorezo gishobora kuba mu gihe cy'ibanze aho guhumuriza abaturage; (4) gutanga imyitozo igamije kandi igira ingaruka nziza mu gihe runaka, mu rwego rwo kongera ubumenyi bw'abaturage ku cyorezo no gupima no kunoza uburyo bw'abaturage bwo gusubiza.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe n'agakoko gashya kitwa SARS-CoV-2 katangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu mezi abiri gusa, ubwo nandikaga iyi nkuru, yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu 50 byo ku isi.
Kubera ko virusi isa na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bikaba bisa cyane hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu bumva ko SARS yagarutse.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na ryo rikomeye mu kurwanya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore kurusha abasaza, kandi ifite ubukana n'urupfu biri hejuru cyane mu bakuru kurusha abakiri bato.
Imfu ziterwa na SARS ziruta iziterwa na COVID-19 (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi nubwo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bo bayikwirakwiza iyo barwaye cyane, bituma gukumira ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bigorana cyane kuruta SARS.
Ibi birasobanura impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane kandi ku buryo bwihuse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibipimo bya RNA bisanzwe bya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kugaragaza ko nta ngaruka mbi ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza virusi.
Ibi byagezweho byongereye cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi.
Iterambere ryihuse mu bushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 ntiryashoboye gukemura ibibazo byinshi by'ingenzi, nk'ibi bikurikira:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo hari ihure ry'ibinyabuzima 96% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-Like CoV ebyiri z'ikinyugunyugu, ntidushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku birondwe.
Ni iyihe nyamaswa yabaye ubwoko bw'ibanze bwo kwanduza virusi ikomoka ku nyamaswa y'inkomoko, ni inyoni zo mu bwoko bw'inguge cyangwa ni abantu?
Iyo tutazi ibisubizo bya # 1 na # 2, ntidushobora guhagarika ubwandu mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza kandi icyorezo gishobora kugaruka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo imiterere ya molekile n'isesengura ry'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuyoboro w'umwuka, hanyuma ikagira ingaruka ku bipimo?
Ese virusi ishobora no kwangiza ingirabuzimafatizo zivuga ACE-2 mu bindi bice by'umubiri?
Ibi bibazo bitarabonerwa ibisubizo bidasobanutse, ntidushobora kubona ibisubizo byabyo mu buryo bwihuse kandi bw'ukuri, kandi ntidushobora kubona uburyo bwiza bwo kuvurwa.
