Ibi bibazo hamwe n'ibindi byinshi bisaba ibisubizo, ariko bishobora gufata igihe.
Ariko uko byagenda kose, nta kundi byagenda uretse guhashya iki cyorezo vuba bishoboka no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
