Kuva mu myaka ibihumbi, koronavirus (CoV) n'ibinyabuzima byayo, harimo n'abantu, byagiye bihinduka bitewe n'impinduka n'imiterere.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bari bazwiho indwara z'ubwoko bumwe (HCoV) ziterwa n'ubwoko bumwe bw'indwara z'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byerekanye ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwangiza kandi bukaba bwica.
Mu mpera za 2019 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, SARS-CoV-2 yongeye kugaragara, kandi twatangajwe n'ubwandu bwayo buhambaye, ariko butari bufite ubwandu bwinshi ugereranyije na SARS-CoV yo mu bwoko bwayo.
Icyorezo cya HCoV ni indwara yandurira mu matungo, bityo ni byiza ko dusobanukirwa inkomoko y'indwara zandurira mu matungo ya HCoV.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka mu birura, aho zitagira ubwandu.
Hari n'izindi ndwara z'ibicurane z'abantu zigize HCoVs zizwi cyane.
Kumenya indyo y'amatungo bishobora kugira ingaruka ku kwirinda indwara z'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire ya COVID-indwara mu nyamaswa bushobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku ndwara ya COVID mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turimo gusuzuma amakuru ahari ku ndwara zirindwi za HCoVs, yibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwazo ndetse n'inkomoko yazo n'ubwandu bw'indwara z'amatungo.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya ubwoko butandukanye bwa HCoVs mu buryo bw'iterambere rya virusi no kongera guhuriza hamwe genome.
Muri iyi nama, hatangijwe ibiganiro ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu.
Byongeye kandi, hakomeje gushyirwa ahagaragara akamaro ko guhindura indyo neza n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku ndwara.
