Izo virusi za RNA zifite genome nini cyane iri hagati ya kilobases 26 na 32 zitwa "COV" kubera ko zigaragara nk'ikamba mu cyuma cya elegitoronike.
Mu buryo bw'imiterere, COVID ifite genomes zitarasenyuka zigira imiterere imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome bigizwe n'ibice bibiri binini by'ibisobanuro byanditse (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihinduka pp1a na pp1ab bihindurwa muri polyproteins.
Izi poroteyine z'amoko menshi zikorwa mu buryo bw'imikorere kugira ngo zitange poroteyine 16 z'imikorere itari iya poroteyine, zitondetse mu buryo bw'imikorere ya poroteyine (NSP1~16).
Ibisigaye bya genome birimo ORF ku maporoteyine y'imiterere, arimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'ubufasha zihariye mu bwoko bwa COV na zo zanditse mu bwoko butandukanye bwa COV.
COVs zigizwe n'ibisekuru bine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV) ukurikije urutonde rw'ibinyabutabire bitandukanye, muri byo icyiciro cya beta-CoV gifite umubare munini wa HCoVs kandi kigabanyijemo ibisekuru bine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo bitanga amakuru y'imiterere y'indwara nyinshi za alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga amakuru y'ibanze kuri virusi za gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, COVID yagiye ihora igenda irenga inzitizi z'ubwoko, ndetse igaragara nk'indwara zikomeye ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hari ubwoko bw'indwara zirindwi z'ubwandu bwa COVID z'abantu (ACOV).
Muri izo virusi harimo alpha-CoVs, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, icyorezo gikomeye cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'imbeho na/cyangwa iseseme.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kumenyekana, ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu barwayi benshi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira (ARDS) no kugaragaza indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814 bwabonetse mu 1960 mu maraso y'abantu barwaye ibicurane.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwari bwaravumbuwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, zitera ibimenyetso byigenga.
Kugeza igihe SARS yadutse, abantu benshi batekerezaga ko HCoV idashobora guteza indwara.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byangiza cyane mu mateka, cyanduje abantu barenga 8,000, hamwe n'ibyago by'urupfu bigera ku 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyatumye haba icyorezo cy'indwara mu Karere ka Arabiya, cyatangiye gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu.
Icyorezo cya HCoV cya 2019 (2019-nCoV) cyaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni cyo cyateye icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Ibyapa by'akaga bikomeje kumvikana kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kizaza.
Indwara zose 7 za ACOV zifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa, yaba inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa karoti, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu rugo.
Ibihamya bitandukanye byashimangiye igitekerezo cy'uko virusi zakomotse ku birura, aho zagiye zifata imiterere kandi ntizigire ubwandu ariko zigaragaza amoko atandukanye y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza n'imyifatire y'abantu mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Iyo umuntu akurikiranye inkomoko y'indwara z'inyamaswa ziterwa na ACOV, asanga amateka kamere, imbaraga zituma habaho ihinduka ry'ubwoko, n'uburyo ibintu bibubuza bigenda bihinduka.
Ibi bizanatuma cyangwa byorohereze gushakisha ibipimo by'ibinyabuzima birinda, bihuza kandi bikomeza SARS-CoV-2, bityo bigire uruhare runini mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi raporo, turatanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'indwara z'amatungo, ubwandu bw'ubwoko n'ubwandu bwa HCOV.
By'umwihariko: Twerekeza ku ngingo rusange zikurikira, tuganira ku buryo virusi z'ababyeyi ba HCoV zisanzwe zitera indwara mu bwoko bwazo bw'imiterere y'imiterere y'imiterere ariko zikaba zitera indwara mu bwoko bushya igihe zanduye mu bwoko bushya.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uburyo bwo guhinduka kwa HCoVs, aho iyo ubwandu bwiyongeye, ubwandu bugabanuka.
Mu kiganiro cyabaye kandi, habaye ibiganiro ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiriho.
Kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30, abantu bamenye ko COVID iboneka mu nyamaswa.
Mbere yo gutandukanya HCoV-229E pathogen B814 mu mazi y'umwotsi y'umurwayi wafashwe n'imbeho, COVID-19 yari yaratoranyijwe mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kumenyekana HCOVs zirindwi.
Mu buryo buhuje n'igihe, igitabo cy'umwimerere cy'ibyavumbuwe na HCoV (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) kizaba ari icy'amakuru kandi cyigisha.
Ubwandu bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwabonetse mu 1966 mu barwayi barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru, nyuma yaho butangira kuvamo uturemangingo tw'ibihaha twa WI-38.
Abanduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo umutwe, gukorora, kuribwa mu muhogo no kuribwa mu muhogo, hamwe n'umuriro mwinshi n'iseru mu bantu bari hagati ya 10-20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yatandukanyijwe n'ibihimba by'imbeba ntoya, nyuma biza gutandukanywa n'imyanya y'ubwonko.
Indwara ya HCoV-OC43 yagaragaje ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'indwara ya HCoV-229E, ariko ntibishobora gutandukanywa mu bimenyetso n'izindi ndwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, urugero nka virusi ya Infuenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byanduye ku isi hose kandi byanduzwa cyane mu gihe cy'itumba mu bihe by'ubushyuhe buke.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kuvura cy'ubwandu bw'izi virusi zombi kiri munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, nyuma y'aho hakamara ibyumweru bibiri umuntu arwaye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitangiye gukora ubushakashatsi, bwagaragaje ko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229e bakunze kugira ibicurane byoroheje.
Gusa hari abantu bake bafite ubwirinzi buke bagaragaza ubwandu bukabije bw'umuyoboro w'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
SARS yitwa "Atipical Pneumonia" ni yo HCoV ya mbere yanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu, kandi impamvu y'ubwandu ni SARS-CoV, ikaba ari yo HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe.
Icyorezo cya mbere cya SARS cyavumbuwe mu mpera za 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 774 bahitanwa na cyo, n'ibindi byorezo 8,096 byamaze kwandura, mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse kuba hari abagerageza cyane, byemezwa ko buri murwayi ashobora gutera indwara ebyiri z'ibanze, ziterwa n'igihe cyo kuvura kiri hagati y'iminsi ine n'iminsi irindwi, kandi ingaruka za virusi zigera ku munsi wa cumi w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV bashobora gutangira bafite ububabare mu mitsi, umutwe, umuriro, ibicurane n'imbeho, nyuma bagahumeka nabi, bagahumeka hanyuma bagahumeka nabi.
Imyanduga y'amaraso, ibibazo byo gupima imikorere y'umwijima no kongera ibinure by'indwara ya Creatinine ni bimwe mu bintu bisanzwe bigaragara mu byumba bya SARS.
Ibyago byo kwangirika kw'imyanya ndangagitsina, gukura kw'utugingo tw'imbere no kwiyongera kwa macrophages na byo byagaragariye mu barwayi ba SARS.
Abagera kuri 20-30% by'abarwayi bakenera ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'umuvuduko w'umwuka nyuma y'aho.
Uretse mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ibihaha, impyiko n'impyiko na byo bishobora kwandura, akenshi bikaba byateza cytoxin storm, ishobora guhitana abantu bafite ubwirinzi buke.
Virusi yatangiriye gutandukanywa n'imyanya ndangagitsina y'umurwayi wavuye mu mujyi wa Guangzhou, yaje muri Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hagiye hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku ndwara ya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yatandukanyijwe n'umwana w'amezi arindwi mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Mu mizo ya mbere, yari yiganje mu bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwaye indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zituma umubiri utagira ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
Indwara iterwa na HCoV-NL63 ikunze kugaragara mu gihe umuntu arwaye ibicurane, uburibwe, umuriro n'imyanda yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Mu kindi cyifuzo cy'ubundi bushakashatsi, ubwo bwandu bw'ubwoko bumwe bw'agakoko bwavumbuwe mu mazi y'uruhu rw'umwana w'amezi umunani wari urwaye umusonga mu Buholandi.
Nubwo byatangiriye mu Buholandi, byamaze gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 ifite uruhare runini mu ndwara z'ubuhumekero zigera kuri 4.7% kandi ko yibasira cyane mu mpeshyi, mu itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'igifu y'uruti rw'umugongo, izwi kandi nka Crohn's.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yatandukanyijwe n'umugabo w'imyaka 71 wari waragiye mu bitaro kubera amapfa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero i Hong Kong.
HCoV-HKU1 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ibihaha ikomeye cyane, harimo na nimoniya n'indwara y'ibihaha zituruka mu baturage.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na yo iboneka ku isi hose, kandi ishobora gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakomeye.
Nubwo izo ndwara zose uko ari enye z'ubwandu bwa HCoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe mu bantu kandi zikaba zitagaragaza ubwandu bukabije, hari ibyago byinshi by'impanuka zituruka ku mpamvu zitazwi, nk'uko byagenze ku zindi ndwara z'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63, ziherutse kuvugwa ko zateye indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, iyo izo HCoVs zigejeje ubushobozi bwo kwandura neza no gukomeza kubaho mu bantu, na zo ziba zidafite ubumara bwinshi cyangwa indwara.
MERS-CoV yatangiriye mu 2012 muri Arabiya Sawudite, itandukanywa n'ibihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari urwaye indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha n'impyiko.
Nubwo abenshi mu banduye bagaragaye mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati, hari abandi bantu baturuka mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi na Tuniziya, batangajwe ko banduye mu buryo bw'ibanze kubera ko bari bahuye cyane.
Icyorezo cya kabiri cyabaye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho abantu 186 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS bisa na SARS, bigaragazwa n'indwara y'ibihaha igenda irushaho gukomera.
Mu buryo butandukanye na SARS, abenshi mu barwayi ba MERS barwaye indwara y'impyiko zidakira, ibintu bidasanzwe ku barwayi ba MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCOV.
