CDC irasaba ko niba hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 ahantu nk'aho bakorera cyangwa mu biraro, ibikoresho byose, nk'amatabuleti, imashini zikora ku gikoresho cyo gukoramo, ibikoresho byo kugenzura kure n'ibyuma bya ATM bikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bikwiye guhuma.
