Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye, basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi kuko kwambara udupfukamunwa bigabanya umubare n'intera utanga mu guhumeka udupfukamunwa dutanga mu kuvuga, gukorora cyangwa gukorora.
