Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi wo muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, avuga ko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora gutuma abantu badakomeza guhura n'abantu bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona, kandi ko iyo umuntu adafite amaguru mazima bishobora gutuma yandura indwara".
OMS itera inkunga abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe gusa bafite ibyago, urugero nk'abita ku bantu banduye COVID-19, kandi yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
CDC itera inkunga ikoreshwa ry'udupfukamunwa tudafite ubumara dukorwa mu myenda muri Amerika. Ubushinwa bwasabye ko abashinzwe ubuzima mu ruhame bakoresha udupfukamunwa tw'imashini tw'imashini zishobora kujugunywa, cyane cyane mu gihe bahuye n'abandi bantu (metero 1 (ibirenge 3) cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bakoresha uburyo bw'ingendo rusange cyangwa mu gihe bari ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima bo muri Thailand barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu rugo no kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza gukaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya bibuza abantu kujya mu ruhame batambaye udupfukamunwa cyangwa se batambaye udupfukamunwa n'umunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, kugira ngo birinde kandi birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yasabye abantu kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye guhaha.
