Kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Taiwan yatangiye gukora udupfukamunwa tugera kuri miliyoni 10 buri munsi, kandi guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abagenzi basabwe kwambara udupfukamunwa mu modoka zo mu ngendo z'amagare n'amabisi.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe bari hanze, kandi abadashobora kugura udupfukamunwa basabwe kuduhimbira mu ngo zabo.
Udupfukamunwa dukoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwirinda kwegerana (nanone byitwa kwegerana mu buryo bw'umubiri) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kugabanya ubwandu bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Muri izo ngamba harimo kwitarura abantu, guhagarika ingendo no gufunga amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitidiyo cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyiraho uburyo bwo kwirinda kwegerana baguma mu rugo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, bakirinda gukorakora mu gihe basuhuzanya n'abandi kandi bakirinda gutandukanya n'abandi.
Guverinoma nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye abantu kwirinda cyane mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Ibigo bya Leta ya Amerika n'ibigo by'ubuzima byahise bigabanya umubare w'abantu bashobora guhurira hamwe, bava ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 izwi muri ako karere) bagera ku bantu 50, hanyuma bagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza abantu babiri cyangwa barenga guhurira ahantu hahurira abantu benshi. Abantu bakuze mu duce turimo ibyorezo by'indwara z'ubwandu n'abafite ubumuga nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubutegetsi, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, CDC iragira inama abantu kuguma mu rugo kuko bahura n'ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'indwara. Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, WHO n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gukoresha ijambo "intera ndende" mu rwego rwo kwirinda "intera ndende" cyangwa intera nyayo mu gihe bagerageza kubana.
Ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "kwirinda" ryatumye abantu batangira kwigunga burundu mu buryo bunyuranye aho gutera inkunga abantu kubana mu buryo bwa rusange. Hari abayobozi batanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo ku isi.
Muri ibyo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana na we gusa kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu bagaragaweho COVID-19 kandi bakekwaho ubwandu basabwe kwiherera mu rugo.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza meza ku bijyanye no kwitarura abantu. Guverinoma nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose batuye mu duce twanduye bashyirwa mu kato.
Ingamba zikomeye cyane zo kwigunga zashyizweho ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi bakaba baherutse gutembera mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kiganjemo ubwandu, basabwe kwicumbikira mu kato iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga guhura.
Gufata ingamba zo kwirinda cyangwa guhashya no guhashya ni byo byonyine bishobora guhashya iki cyorezo.
Gutegeka ikwirakwira ry'indwara bikorwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana abantu banduye, kubashyira mu kato, no gutegura uburyo bwo kubarinda no kubaha inkingo kugira ngo bakwirakwize mu bandi bantu.
Iyo ikwirakwira ry'indwara ridashobora guhagarikwa, ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo zirakorwa: Ingamba zo kugabanya umuvuduko w'ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ibi byombi bishobora guhuza mu kurwanya ikwirakwira n'igabanya ikwirakwira.
Gufata ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, nko kugabanya umubare w'ibinyabuzima byongera kubyara munsi ya 1, ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi mu gutegura icyorezo.
Ibi bituma ikibazo cy'uburwayi kigabanuka, kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu bintu by'ubuvuzi bidakoreshwa mu kwirinda icyorezo, harimo gukaraba intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwicungira ukwa bonyine, gufunga amashuri, kubuza abantu guteranira hamwe, gushishikariza abaturage kwemera no kubishyira mu bikorwa, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, mu gihe hari n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubuziranenge bigamije kwirinda ikumiro, ndetse no gusukura aho abantu batuye. Mu gihe icyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera, Ubushinwa bwashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu mijyi yose no gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi na byo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangiye gukora ibizamini byinshi no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi iraburira abantu kwirinda kwimuka kw'abantu banduye.
Singapore yafashije mu buryo bw'amafaranga abantu biyemeje kwicamo ibice, kandi igahana abatabishoboye.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa tw'amaso kandi ihana abantu batunze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Kurikiza urugero rw'u Bwongereza na Loni, hari imbogamizi zikomeye mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo (kugabanya umuvuduko w'ikirere, ntabwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugihagarika (kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo).
Gushyiraho gahunda nziza zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakeneye serivisi z'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3 no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bishobora gutuma hapfa abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi kandi bigashyira imbaraga nyinshi ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Gukumira cyangwa gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi bishobora kuba ari byo by'ingenzi ariko bigomba gukomeza kugeza igihe virusi ikwirakwiriye mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari ubwa mbere), kuko iyo mikoro igabanyijwe, kwandura bishobora kongera kwiyongera.
Gushyiraho ingamba ndende zo gukumira cyangwa guhashya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo bitera igihombo mu bukungu no mu mibereho y'abaturage.
Nta miti yihariye ya virusi yemewe ya COVID-19 ihari ariko hari ingamba zo kuyikora harimo no gupima imiti iboneka.
Kunywa imiti ya common cold, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bihagije bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Kugira ngo umuntu akire indwara, ashobora gukenera umwuka wa ogisijeni, uruvange rw'amazi mu mitsi ye, cyangwa se akeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma ingaruka ziba mbi kurushaho.
Hari imiti myinshi yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa virusi iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS yavuze kandi ko "imiti gakondo n'iy'iwacu" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-2.
OMS yavuze ko kongera ubushobozi no kunoza serivisi z'ubuzima ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ari byo by'ibanze mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ibiro bya ECDC na OMS by'akarere k'u Burayi byatanze amabwiriza yo gushyira mu bikorwa ibikoresho biboneka mu bitaro no mu buvuzi bw'ibanze mu byiciro bitandukanye birimo kwibanda ku serivisi za laboratwari zo gupima COVID-19, kureka uburyo busimbura aho bishoboka, gushyira mu kato abanduye COVID-19 no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwivuza mu buryo bw'indembe binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zitanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku byerekeye aho umuntu wa mbere (wavuzwe ko ari umuganga wa zeru) ashobora kuba yarabonywe.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyi virusi ya Corona ashobora kuba yaranduye Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera.
Benshi bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibikoresho byo mu nyanja bya Hunan, aho bagurishaga n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa nk'izo, cyangwa mu yandi magambo, ko ari inyamaswa z'inkomoko. Itsinda ry'abarwayi ba pneumonie z'impamvu zitazwi, basanze ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi bavurirwa mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei na Dr Zhang Jishian, wabwiye Wuhan Jishian CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, bari baragabishije bagenzi babo ku bijyanye na "SARS-Tatsum coronavirus".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Lee Wenling, bari barahawe umuburo na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi, Mama Fan, yahawe umuburo ukaze n'abamusumbaga kubera ko yari yarabibabwiye.
Komisiyo ya Wuhan Municipal yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo ku baturage maze imenyesha WHO.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan batangiye iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, batangaza ko hari abantu benshi bafite indwara y'ibicurane itaramenyekana, kandi mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, imibare y'abanduye yiyongeraga kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Kubera ko ubwandu buterwa n'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa n'uko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'aho gari ya moshi zihurira, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, mu Bushinwa hemejwe ko hari abantu bagera ku 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma y'aho agaragaza ko abantu 6174 bari bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa mbere kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari zashize u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku rutonde rw'ibihugu bifite umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Kugeza ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 ni bo bamaze kwandura ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abarenga 364.000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byamaze kugaragaza nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cy'isi mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byashyizeho imipaka ku ngendo z'abantu no kugenzura imipaka.
Ibisubizo ku rwego rw'igihugu birimo ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo (amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kuguma aho uri hose no gufunga) hamwe no gufunga abantu. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, cyangwa 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu buhungiro.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, umubare wiyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 mu minsi ibiri - kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejweho COVID-19 yagaragaye i Wuhan mbere ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, umuntu umwe utari wemejwe yagaragaye ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jishian yasanze hari abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'umusonga ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma yaho ibitaro bye byabwiye Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere bya Jenoside byakozwe ku bantu bari barwaye ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza byerekanye ko hari virusi ya Corona imeze nka SARS.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Komini ya Wuhan yasohoye itangazo rigenewe abaturage.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Ubwo iyi nkuru yatangazwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'igipolisi ko bashobora gukwirakwiza ibihuha by'ibinyoma ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta bimenyetso bifatika bigaragaza ko abantu banduye.
Mu minsi ya nyuma ya Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye, nyuma y'aho buvugwa na Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Icyiswe "igikorwa cy'isuku cya mbere kinini mu mateka y'abantu" cyatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama, gihagarika ingendo z'imbere n'inyuma muri Wuhan, nyuma y'aho cyongerewe mu mijyi 15 yose ya Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zari zarabuzanyijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya wa China (ku ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi batangaje kandi ko hari hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo byitwa Hushenshan Hospital, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Mu rwego rwo kwita ku barwayi benshi, hatangijwe indi bitaro, Lichenchen Hospital.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bibanza bya Wuhan nk'ibigo by'inama n'inyubako nk'ibibuga by'imikino mu bitaro by'agateganyo.Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera iminsi mikuru yo mu rugaryi.
Amashuri n'amashuri yisumbuye muri icyo gihugu byafunzwe.
Mu karere ka Hong Kong na Macao, ingamba nyinshi zafashwe, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu bice byinshi by'u Bushinwa, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukora ku buryo bwa kure.
Ingendo zo mu gihugu no hanze ya Hubei zarahagaritswe.
Imodoka zitwara abantu mu ruhame zahindutse, kandi inzu ndangamurage zo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa zarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Imikoranire y'abaturage yashyizwe mu kato mu mijyi myinshi, kandi abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bageramiwe n'ibihano byo kujya hanze. Mu kwezi kwa gatatu ubwo icyorezo cyageraga ku isi, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi igera mu Bushinwa ivuye mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yategetse ko abagenzi bose mpuzamahanga baza mu mujyi bose bashyirwa mu kato k'iminsi 14. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, hari umuntu umwe gusa wari waranduye mu gihugu mu minsi itanu ishize, wari uturutse i Istanbul mu mujyi wa Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'ubwoko bushya bwahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyigaruriwe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, muri Hubei, uretse i Wuhan, hashyizweho ingamba zo koroshya ingendo nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho Guma mu Rugo. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko visa cyangwa ibyangombwa by'ubwenegihugu bifite agaciro bizasubikwa nyuma ya 28 Werurwe, kandi ntiyatanga ibisobanuro ku gihe gahunda yo guhagarika izarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba muri ambasade cyangwa muri ambasade y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije gufungura ubucuruzi n'inganda ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku nganda. Komite y'Igihugu yatangaje ko umunsi wo kwibuka uzatangira ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi za mu gitondo, n'iminota itatu y'agahenge mu gihugu cyose.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, byemejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, byatewe ahanini n'ikoraniro ry'idini rishya, ari ryo Shincheonji Church of Jesus, mu mujyi wa Daegu.
Abantu bari baje gusura Shincheonji i Wuhan Degu, bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, abantu 1261 muri 9336 bari muri Kiliziya bagaragaje ibimenyetso, ni ukuvuga hafi 13%. Koreya y'Epfo yatanze umuburo wo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Korea yatangaje ko imaze kugira abarwayi barenga 2000 b'iyi ndwara, ku ya 29 Gashyantare, yari imaze kwiyongera igera ku 3150.
Inzego zose z'igisirikare cya Koreya y'Epfo zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu b'ingabo z'igihugu bagaragayeho ubwandu bw'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda ikomeye kandi iteguwe neza ku isi yo gupima abantu benshi, gushyira mu kato abantu banduye, kubakurikirana, no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye na bo.
Muri ubwo buryo bwo gupima harimo kwandikisha ibimenyetso by'indwara z'abantu bavuye mu mahanga bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni zigendanwa, gupima virusi mu modoka mbere yo kuva mu modoka, nyuma y'umunsi umwe, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'ifitwe ingaruka nziza mu kugenzura icyorezo aho guhagarika imijyi yose. Mu mizo ya mbere, Perezida Moon Jae-in yatumye umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo utagira aho uhuriye n'ibibazo by'ubukene.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo kumukurikirana cyangwa kumushimira kubera ibyo babona ko ari uburyo Leta ikoresha mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu byumweru bine, wabonetse ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru yo ku ya 1 Mata avuga ko Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ibihugu 121 bitandukanye byo gufasha mu gupima virusi.
