Ingamba zatangajwe na leta mu ntangiriro z'iyi gahunda, harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize mu bikorwa miliyari eshanu z'amanyarwanda zo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'icyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazaba mu kato.
Nubwo hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi, ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imijyi zakomeje kugeza nyuma y'umwaka mushya wa Navroz w'Abaperesi.
Mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020, Iran yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira rya virusi nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Hagati aho, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abanduye kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko iki cyorezo gikomeye cyane kurusha abanduye 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe ubwo 23 mu bayigize 290 bageragezaga bagasanga baranduye.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura nta mpamvu n'imwe abantu bafunzwe bazira ko batumvikana mu mahoro, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo abandi bantu bakwiriye.
Yavuze kandi ko ibigo bifunze, nk'ibigo byo gufunga abantu, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije, bishobora kugira ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, umubare munini mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani coronavirus yari ifite ubwandu bushya 50 buri saha, n'urupfu rumwe buri minota 10.
Umukozi wa OMS yavuze ko Iran ishobora kuba ifite abanduye barenze inshuro eshanu abo imaze gutangaza.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kuba byaratumye icyo gihugu kidabasha guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, harimo na Iran, byoroherezwa mu bijyanye n'ingamba z'ubukungu.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyatangiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama ubwo abagenzi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izigaruka mu Bushinwa kandi itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, mu ntara ya Lombardy, havumbuwe icyiciro cy'abantu banduye COVID-19 batandukanye nyuma y'aho hatangiriye icyiciro cy'abantu 16 bemejwe. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigena ko abantu basaga 50000 bo mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bashyirwa mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yavuze ko nta muntu uzinjira cyangwa ngo ave mu gace kagwiririwe n'icyo cyorezo.
"Ku ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifunga burundu kubera ko mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100".
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kubera mu kibuga gikinze kugeza mu kwezi kwa kane, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe, Conte, yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bifungwa, uretse amaduka manini n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abadamu, Abaganga, Abashya n'Abajyanama (SIAARTI) cyasohoye amategeko y'ubuvuzi asaba imyitwarire y'abana bo mu ngo bashobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze u Bushinwa bufata icyemezo cyo kuba igihugu cya mbere ku isi cyahitanwe na coronavirus, aho cyagize abantu 3,405 bapfuye kubera icyorezo.
Byatangajwe ko ku ya 22 Werurwe, Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare mu Butaliyani zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Mu Butaliyani, kugeza ku itariki ya 5 Mata, hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128,948, hapfuye abantu 158,87, kandi abantu 218,15 barakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru bo mu Butaliyani hamwe no kunanirwa gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu bishobora kuba byaratumye hapfa benshi.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyagaragaye ko aricyo cyoroheje mu bindi bihugu byanduye, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa kwitarura abaturage bayo.
Ibi byatumye guverinoma inengwa ko idasobanukiwe umuvuduko n'uburemere bwo gusubiza ibibazo abantu bahura nabyo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje itangazo risaba abantu kwirinda ingendo zose zidakenewe no kwifatanya n'abandi, asaba abantu gukorera mu rugo igihe bishoboka no kwirinda ahantu nko mu kabari, muri resitora no muri za sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho kwidagadura nko mu tubari no mu tubyiniro h'imikino hakwiye gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi ko hatanzwe 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi kugeza ku gipimo cya £2500 buri kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri mu gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, nko kubuza abantu barenze babiri guteranira hamwe, ingendo no kugabanya imirimo yo hanze gusa nk'ibikenewe.
Ibi bitandukanye n'ibya mbere, aho amategeko yashoboraga gutuma abapolisi bafatirwa ibihano no gusenya imbaga.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwarahagaritswe, usibye ubucuruzi bwafashwe nk'ubw'ingenzi cyane, harimo amasoko akomeye, amaduka y'ubuvuzi, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, za peteroli n'amategura.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho COVID-19 yemejwe ku ya 20 Mutarama muri Leta ya Washington yo mu Majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, ku muntu wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Ku ya 29 Mutarama, Inteko Rusange y'Ibikorwa bya Coronavirus yashyizweho.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ibihe bidasanzwe by'ubuzima rusange, ndetse bunashyiraho amategeko abuza abagenzi kuva mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo cy'ubutegetsi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange, ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Ariko kandi, uko icyo gihe icyorezo cyari giteye mu by'ukuri ntibyari bizwi neza, kubera ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika umubare w'abantu bageragezwaga wari muke.
Ibizamini byatewe n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini bidakora neza byakozwe na leta ya federasiyo muri Gashyantare, ibikoresho by'ibizamini bitemewe na leta (byakozwe n'ibigo by'amashuri, ibigo n'ibitaro) ntibyemewe na leta ya federasiyo kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, kandi abantu bari bafite ibisabwa by'ibanze byo gukoreshwa mu gupima kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma yaho hakenewe inyandiko ya muganga).
Ku ya 27 Mutarama, ikinyamakuru Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari hasigaye ibizamini 4000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari ibipimo 14,000 byafashwe.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko abantu bafite ibimenyetso byinshi n'amabwiriza y'abaganga yo kubapima, byatwara amasaha kugeza ku minsi kugira ngo bapimwe. Igihe urupfu rwa mbere muri Amerika rwatangazwaga i Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko muri leta hari ibihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyahise cyakurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritswe ku ya 3 Werurwe, amashuri yose yo mu gihugu yose arafungwa mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'ibyorezo zo muri Imperial College i Londres zatanze inama ku byitezwe muri Amerika ku ngaruka iyi virusi nshya ya Corona ishobora kugira ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ritanga inkunga y'ingoboka ya $8.3 ku bigo bya leta kugira ngo bihangane n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yahagaritse ingendo z'abakozi, avanaho inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukora bava mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 y'ingendo zihagaritswe kuva mu Bwongereza kugera mu Burayi bwose guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, bwarushijeho gukomanga, bwuzuzaho Ubwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe by'ibiza, bituma haboneka n'amafaranga ya Leta kugira ngo iki cyorezo kiveho.
Mu ntangiriro z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha y'akazi kugira ngo bigabanyirize ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, ibihugu byose bigera kuri 50 n'Akarere ka Columbia byari byemejwe ko byanduye. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko kureba kure bigaragara ko ari byo byatuma habaho itandukaniro, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, Umujyi wa New York wari ufite abarwayi 32308, kandi abantu 672 barapfuye bazize virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko zifite abarwayi benshi kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi cyemeje ko cyanduye coronavirus, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, Amerika yari ifite abarwayi 4000335 bamaze kwemezwa, hamwe n'abantu 12841.
Amakuru yo ku wa 30 Werurwe avuga ko Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yongereye amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kure y'abandi kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitaro 1000 bwageze i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yatangaje ko imaze gutanga impfu 884 mu masaha 24 gusa.
Umubare w'abanduye muri leta ya New York warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kubera gupfobya akaga n'ubufatanye n'ibiro bya Mike Pence, Visi Perezida, mu gutanga itangazo n'ibinyamakuru ku baturage bijyanye na virusi, bigenzura ubutumwa butangwa n'abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi.
Muri rusange, imyumvire y'ubutegetsi bwa Trump ku bibazo yari yiganjemo imyumvire y'urujijo n'ivangura.
