Isesengura ry'ibipimo by'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu kwerekana icyorezo no kumenya urugero rw'icyorezo, kandi byatangajwe mu kwezi kwa mbere hagati muri The Journal of Travel Medicine.
