OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS hagati ya 2002-2004 ubwo abayobozi b'Abashinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye imihati yo kurwanya no kugenzura iki cyorezo ihagarara, n'ikibazo kiriho aho Leta nkuru itanga amakuru buri gihe kugirango birinde ubwoba mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'izuba.
Mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'abategetsi bo mu Burayi cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye OMS, Goden Gyi, yavuze ko iyi nama ya OMS itari ikwiye kandi ko ari ikimenyetso cy'uko icyorezo cyakwirakwira mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abanduye, avuga ko ari "ikintu kidasanzwe mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange".Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma y'ibimenyetso byemejwe by'ubwandu bw'abantu mu Bushinwa no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange mpuzamahanga (Public Health Emergency) mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye ku isi mu 2009, ubwo ku nshuro ya mbere OMS yashyiragaho ingamba za PHIEC mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC iterwa n'akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite ubukungu buciriritse aho inzego z'ubuzima zidakora neza.
Mu gusubiza ku bihano ku ngendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitari ngombwa zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza gushyiraho ibihano ku bucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha mu kwitegura mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, aho yabonye ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu mu gufasha ibihugu bifite uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye nubwo byatangira kwandura.
Tedrosini yakomeje avuga ko "turi abanyembaraga gusa nk'urwego rwacu rw'ingingo rukomeye cyane" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura ejo". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, yise iki cyorezo COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gushyira imbaraga zose z'umuryango w'abibumbye mu guhangana.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ubukene ryatangiye gukora, ryemerewe guhuza ibikorwa byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bishobora gutuma ryibanda ku bikorwa by'ubuzima, bityo izindi nzego zikoresha ubumenyi bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu, imibereho myiza n'iterambere.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa ba WHO riyobowe n'u Bushinwa ryatangijwe kugira ngo ritange impuguke mpuzamahanga na WHO zifasha mu gucunga mu Bushinwa, kandi zitange amahugurwa ku buremere bw'icyorezo n'ubwandu, kandi zitange inama n'inzego z'ibanze ku rwego rw'igihugu, kandi zisuye akarere k'imijyi n'icyaro ku rwego rw'intara no mu gihugu kugirango zisuzume ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko "isi ikeneye gukora byinshi mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ibikorwa ryihariye kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ubushakashatsi ku isi hose ku kaga ka coronavirus buzazamurwa buva ku "burenze" bujya ku rwego rwo hejuru rwo kugabisha no kugenzura akaga.
Umuyobozi w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Mike Ryan, mu itangazo yatanze, yavuze ko iki ari igihe cyo gusuzuma uko ibintu byifashe ku butegetsi bwose ku isi.
Yongeyeho ko uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana na byo buzafasha isi kwirinda ibibi cyane.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adashishikariza abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage gutangaza ko iki ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose, avuga ko gutangaza ibi byaba bivuze ko twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'ubuyobozi yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu n'uburemere bw'icyorezo n'ingaruka mbi z'ibikorwa by'ubudehe". OMS iri kunengwa cyane kubera uburyo ikomeje gukemura ikibazo cy'icyorezo cyugarije isi, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu mu buzima bw'abaturage no kugishyira mu byiciro by'icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Mu bitekerezo by'amacakubiri harimo n'icyemezo cyo kwegura kwa Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi w'ishami rya OMS, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu zisaga icumi zasabye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Abo bahanga bavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gutabara ubuzima kandi ko ari inshingano za leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura ibikoresho cyangwa kubura ubwisungane mu kwivuza bidakwiye gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo gutandukanya itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abari mu matsinda mato, abarokotse burundu, abavuye mu byabo, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abafashwe, impunzi n'abandi bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga biri guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'ubukungu n'iterambere ryatangije urubuga rutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku migambi yo guhangana n'isi yose, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku migambi yo kongerera imbaraga inzego z'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku gukemura ingaruka z'ibihano byo gufunga no kugenzura ingendo, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo gukurikirana gahunda z'igihugu, kandi kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga kuri buri kimwe no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe cyane n'abaminisitiri ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, UK Cabinet Office Michael Glowe n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil, Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, ku buryo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi benshi b'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) ku rwego rw'intara birukanywe kubera uburyo bakemuye ibikorwa byo kwigunga mu Bushinwa rwagati, byerekana ko batabyishimiye kubera ibisubizo by'ishyaka rya politiki ririho muri ako gace.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko iyo myigaragambyo yari igamije kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, bashyigikiye igitekerezo cy'ubucuruzi ko COVID-19 yatangiriye muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani, bahakana ko icyorezo cya mbere cya coronavirus cyavuye i Wuhan.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus "Virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan", buvuga ko "ibanga ry'Ubushinwa ryatumye virusi ikomeza gukwira ku buryo yahindutse icyorezo ku isi" kandi bamwe mu bayobozi bakomeje gushinja ko ari amacakubiri n'uko "ubutegetsi bw'igihugu cyabo bwananiwe guhashya icyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye telegrafe ya leta ya Amerika yari irimo ubutumwa buvuga ku buryo bwo kuyobya umwanzi, bushobora kuba bwatangiriye mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, ivuga ko iyo gahunda "ari iy'Ubushinwa".
Turabwirwa kugerageza no gutangaza ubwo butumwa mu buryo ubwo aribwo bwose, haba mu nama z'abanyamakuru, mu biganiro byo kuri televiziyo, n'ibindi.Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko kugerageza kohereza imfashanyo mu bice byugarijwe na virusi by'Ubushinwa ari uburyo bwo kwamamaza ubutegetsi bw'isi.
Umuyobozi wa politiki y'amahanga ya EU, Josep Borel, yatanze umuburo ko "Politiki y'ubwisanzure" irimo ibintu bya gipolitiki birimo no guharanira ubutegetsi.
Borrell yavuze kandi ko Ubushinwa bwarimo kohereza ubutumwa bukomeye ko ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe kurusha Amerika.
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano ku bihugu bya Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse buvuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo kuri Venezuela na Iran.
Imfashanyo ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 10 000 yagombaga kohereza muri Cuba yahagaritswe ku ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano bya Amerika.
Abategetsi ba Amerika na bo bashinjwa ko bahinduye imfashanyo bahaga ibindi bihugu bakajya kuziha ibihugu byabo.
Hari kandi ibindi bihugu byavuze ko hari impaka ku myambaro, urugero nk'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi; Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero bibarirwa mu magana byari byateguwe na Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yashinje Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi kutagira ubumwe n'Ubutaliyani bwazahajwe n'icyorezo.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwashubije mu buryo bw'impande zombi".
Nta gushidikanya, ibyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubumwe bw'i Burayi".
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yavuze ko ingabo z'u Burusiya ziteganya kohereza mu Butaliyani ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, imodoka zihariye z'ubuvuzi n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa, cyishingikirije ku "miterere ya politiki yo hejuru" itaramenyekana, cyavuze ko 80% by'imfashanyo z'Uburusiya zari zidakenewe cyangwa zitari zifite akamaro kanini ku Butaliyani.
Uwo mushinjacyaha yavuze ko u Burusiya bwakoze ibikorwa by'ubushotoranyi bwo "gushishikariza abantu gukora ibikorwa bya politiki n'ibya dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'Umunyamabanga w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani, Luigi de Mayo, bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru kandi barashimira.
Uburusiya na bwo bwo bwohereje indege zitwara ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Piskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] aha inkunga bagenzi be ba Amerika, azirikana ko igihe ibigo by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byo muri Amerika bizagenda byihuta, na byo bizishyura mu gihe bibikeneye".
NATO yateganyije gahunda ya Defender 2020 y'ingabo mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, ikaba ari gahunda nini cyane ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangiye.
Kate Hudson, umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, yanenze gahunda ya Defender 2020 agira ati "muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, iyi gahunda ntabwo ihungabanya ingabo za Amerika gusa n'ibindi bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, ahubwo ihungabanya n'abaturage b'ibihugu bakoreramo". Guverinoma ya Irani yagize ingaruka zikomeye kuri iyi virusi, kandi abadepite bagera kuri 20 barayanduye, kimwe n'abanyapolitiki 15 bakorera cyangwa bahoze bayikorera.
Perezida wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yandikiye ibaruwa y'abantu benshi ku bayobozi b'isi ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo guhangana n'icyorezo kubera ko Amerika itagifite ubushobozi bwo kugera ku isoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibyo yafatiriwe. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ifata ingamba zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize zirimo gahunda y'ubuzima rusange, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango uhembwa, n'amafaranga menshi yo kwita ku buzima rusange.
Abasesengura politiki bavuze ko ibyo bizagira ingaruka mbi ku matora ya Perezida Donald Trump mu 2020. Iki cyorezo cy'icyorezo cyatumye umubano w'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo uhagarara.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati iteye amakenga kandi idafatika yo gushyira abantu mu kato" y'Ubuyapani ubwo yatangazaga ko abantu bose bavuye muri Koreya y'Epfo bazashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce leta izatoranya.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo watangiye ufite ibitekerezo bitandukanye cyangwa by'ubwigunge ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo gushinja Moon ko yafashwe nabi n'ubutegetsi kubera uburyo yakoresheje mu guhashya icyorezo cya Chuki, cyangwa se bamushimira cyane.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo by'ubujiji bavuga ko ibyo bishobora guha ubutegetsi uburyo bwo gukomeza gutegeka.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yabo yatoye itegeko ryemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe wabo Viktor Orban gutegeka igihe kitarangiye, gusesa inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora no kurinda abantu bakekwaho gukwirakwiza amakuru atari yo kuri virusi, no guhangana n'ikibazo cya leta.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatewe n'ibintu byinshi birimo ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa bitangwa n'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho byo guhangana n'icyorezo ku isi, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhangayika no guhungabanya inganda n'ingendo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatangaje ko hari ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi batabasha kubikora.
Mu bice byinshi, abantu bagurishije ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya, bituma ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi y'ibyatsi bizimira mu isoko, bituma habaho ubukene.
Ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga byibanze ku bikoresho bya elegitoroniki byiburiwe ku gihe cyo gutumiza ibicuruzwa.
Dukurikije umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibisabwa ku bikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibiciro byazamutse bikubye inshuro 20 ugereranyije n'uko byari bisanzwe, kandi ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi byatewe n'ikibazo cy'ibyumweru bine kugeza kuri bitandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikena ku isi hose, kandi OMS iraburira ko bishobora gushyira ubuzima bw'abakozi b'ubuzima mu kaga.
Muri Australia, icyorezo cy'icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Daigu babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byabo mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye amaduka manini atabasha kubona ibiribwa by'abana, maze leta ya Australia irabyanga. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu gace ka Wuhan hari abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 kandi hari n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, utwo duce twombi twaracitse intege kubera ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ingenzi n'ibikoresho by'ibanze zagize icyo zigeraho, bityo birinda ibura ry'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Ibiciro by'ibiribwa bishobora kuzamuka, nk'uko byemejwe n'abahagarariye inganda, ariko nta gaciro gahanitse kabonetse kubera umusaruro w'ibiribwa mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Mu gihe ibigo by'ubucuruzi byari byarabuze amasahani y'ibiribwa byari iby'igihe gito mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafunguye ibigega by'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani, hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi kubika ibiribwa mu gihe habaye ibyago.
Ubushinwa ni bwo bwatewe n'ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'isi, nk'uko ikinyamakuru kimwe cyabitangaje ku ya 16 Werurwe, kivuga ko ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwagize ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020, bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta y'Ubushinwa zo guhashya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20.5%.
Ubushinwa bw'ibanze ni ubukungu bw'ingenzi kandi ni ikigo cy'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi kibonwa nk'ikibazo gikomeye ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu, yavuze ko ibiciro bizakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe ibizavamo bizamenyekana.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hari abahanga batangaje ko ubukungu bw'isi buzagabanuka bitewe n'iki cyorezo, buzaba bwarenze urugero ku buryo bwari buhari mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, ivuga ko ingaruka ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi yose ishobora kuba miliyari $300+ kandi ishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu by'ibihangange mu gutumiza peteroli (OPEC) uvuga ko ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli byatangiye kugwa cyane kubera ko ubukene bw'ibikomoka kuri peteroli bwari bugabanutse cyane mu Bushinwa.
Ibigo by'imigabane ku isi byaguye ku itariki ya 24 Gashyantare, bitewe n'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, imibare itandukanye y'imigabane ya Amerika, harimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 na Dow Jones Industrial Average, yagaragaje ko yagabanutse cyane kuva mu 2008, maze Dow ikagwaho amanota 1191, ikaba ari yo yagabanutse cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ubukungu bw'isi mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo uko ari bitatu byafunze munsi ya 10% muri iki cyumweru.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje ko u Bushinwa bufite inguzanyo y'igihugu ariko ikomeza kubona ibintu nabi.
Imicungire y'imigabane yongeye kugwa nyuma y'ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi bumva ko ubukungu buzahinduka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohammed Al Ariyan yashimye ingamba za Leta n'Ibanki Nkuru zafashe mu gihe cy'ibiza.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zitabiriye vuba cyane kurusha uko byagenze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryo mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo niwo mugabane wugarijwe cyane n'ibihano by'ingendo, aho ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu ho gutemberera hafunze, ndetse na leta zigira inama abantu kutagira aho bajya hirya no hino ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko ingendo z'indege nyinshi zataye agaciro kubera ko hari abantu bake cyane, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe FlyBee, ikigo cy'indege cyo mu Bwongereza, cyahagaritswe.
Ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'ubwato bwageze ku rwego rutazwi.
Ibigo byinshi by'indege n'amato byarahagaritswe.
Iki cyorezo cyaje mu gihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, ari cyo Chunyan.
Ibihe byinshi by'imyiyereko myinshi byahagaritswe na guverinoma z'igihugu n'iz'ibanze harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, ndetse n'ibigo byigenga byitaye ku bantu bose bifunga amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga hatera ingendo nk'ahitwa Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'umwaka mushya w'izuba n'ahantu nyaburanga hatandukanye byafunzwe kugira ngo hatagira abantu benshi bahurira hamwe, harimo n'umujyi wa Forbidden City n'ibirori by'imana gakondo i Beijing.
Abategetsi mu ntara 24, mu mirenge 31 n'uturere tw'u Bushinwa, bongereye iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ahantu henshi bakorera hatagomba gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice bigira 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yongereye cyane uburyo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cy'indwara, itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika ibirori by'umwaka mushya.
Mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo, umubare w'abakiriya bajya guhaha ku bacuruzi wagabanutseho 40%.
Muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, byagabanutseho hagati ya 50% na 60%.
Ibi byatumye abagura ibicuruzwa mu bigo by'ubucuruzi bya Piy Hindat bagabanukaho 33-43% muri Gashyantare ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze mu kwezi kwa gatatu.
Abikorera mu bigo by'ubucuruzi ku isi hose basabye ko hakorwa ingamba nyinshi zirimo kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe mu bagenzi no guhagarika ibikorwa. Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo ivuga ko ubukene bwatewe n'icyorezo buzatuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 bo muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo bagwa mu bukene bukabije kurusha uko bari kumera iyo hataza kubaho icyorezo.
Mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera hafi kuri miliyoni eshanu batakaje akazi muri Mutarama na Gashyantare.
Abakozi bo mu cyaro b'abimukira bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa bafatiwe mu mazu yabo mu ntara z'imbere cyangwa bafatiwe mu ntara ya Hubei. Mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo maze basaba ubufasha bwa leta.
