Ibizamini byo mu mavuriro bya Coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura virusi no kumenya antibiyotike ziterwa no kwitabira ubwandu.
Kuba virusi iri mu isuzuma byemezwa na RT-PCR, ishakisha RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni cyihariye kandi cyakozwe mu buryo bwo gutahura gusa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ko umuntu aherutse kwandura cyangwa ko yanduye.
Ibizamini bya antibiyotike birashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara (serologie) no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini bya antibiyotike bigaragaza umubare w'abantu barwaye, harimo abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso, kugira ngo tubyumve neza.
Ibizamini bizatuma abantu bashobora kumenya neza umubare w'abapfa n'urwego rw'abanduye.
Kubera ibizamini bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini hagati y'ibihugu ku bipimo byakozwe.
Ibi bishobora no kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, kandi mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bishobora kuba bidashyize mu gaciro.
Imyandikire y'igihe cy'ukuri ishobora kugeragezwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo bya nasopharyngeal swab cyangwa ibipimo by'amacandwe, hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa RRT-PCR.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igikorwa cyo gupima amacandwe ya RT-PCR cyemeza gusa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo ikagenda ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Mu gihe abantu banduye bapimwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, uburyo bumwe ni ukuvana ibipimo mu mwuka mu buryo bwimbitse binyuze mu cyuma cyo kunyoha, cyangwa se gukoresha ibipimo byo mu gihe cyo gukorora.
Muri Mutarama 2020, ikigo cy'ubugiraneza cy'i Berlin cyatangije imwe mu ncuro za mbere za PCR zikoresha uburyo bwa Real-Time Reverse Transcription Polymer Chain Reaction (RRT-PCR) kandi ni yo yari ishingiro ry'ibipimo 250,000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Cogenebiotech cyakoze icyiciro cyo kwa muganga, PCR-based SARS-CoV-2 detector kit (Powercheck coronavirus).
Iki kizamini cyerekana umugera wa "E" usanganywe na virusi ya Corona yose ya beta, hamwe n'umugera wa RdRp wihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2. BGI Group yari imwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse na National Medical Products Administration y'Ubushinwa ku gikoresho cy'ubushakashatsi cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR mu Bushinwa. Muri Amerika, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) ikomeje gutanga ibikoresho byo gupima 2019-novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe nyacyo-PCR binyuze mu ikigo mpuzamahanga gishinzwe kurwanya indwara (Research Resources).
Kimwe mu bice bitatu by'ibanze by'ibipimo bya kera by'ibipimo byatewe n'ikigeragezo cy'ikosa ry'ibanze ryateje ingaruka zidahamye kandi bibangamira ibizamini muri CDC i Atlanta; bigatuma ingero nkeya ku munsi zigera ku 100 zikorwa neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, ibizamini bikoresha ibintu bibiri ntibyari byemewe, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibigo by'ibanze n'ibya leta ntibyemerewe gutangira gukora ibizamini.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti muri Amerika cyemeje iki kizamini mu buryo bw'ibanze. Ibitaro by'ubucuruzi muri Amerika byatangiye kugerageza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko hari ibipimo bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR bizatangwa mu gihugu hose.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020, Quest Diagnostics yashyize hanze ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu gihugu hose.
Nta gihagararo cyatanzwe ku gipimo; igiteranyo cy'ibipimo n'imikorere bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubwandu bw'indwara n'ikoranabuhanga mu Burusiya, Vector, ni cyo cyakoze ikizamini cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki cyemezo cyanditswe na Federal Service for Healthcare Monitoring. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Mayo Clinic yateguye iki cyemezo cyo gupima ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 ku gipimo kinini, bityo ikemerera imashini imwe gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye Abbott Laboratories uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) rwo gukora ibizamini kuri Abbott's M2000 System; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'uru mbere kuri Hologic, LabCorp na ThermoFisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cefid yahawe EUA na FDA mu buryo nk'ubwo, ku buryo igeragezwa rishobora gukorwa mu minota 45.
FDA yemeje ikizamini gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingufu za nucleic acid (isothermal nucleic acid amplification) aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba uruhererekane rw'ingendo z'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byemejwe mu minota itanu n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Kugeza ubu, muri Amerika hari ibikoresho bigera ku 18,000, Abbott ikaba yiteze ko izagera ku gipimo cyo gukora ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi.Ikizamini gikoresha umuti wa monoclonal ukingira indwara, gihuza by'umwihariko poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N protein) ya coronavirus, kirimo gukorwa muri Tayiwani, kandi byitezwe ko kizatanga ibisubizo nk'iby'ibizamini bya vuba bya influenza mu minota iri hagati ya 15 na 20.
Mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, isuzuma ry'amakuru ryavuze ko "X-ray z'igituza zidafite akamaro kenshi mu gusuzuma indwara mu gihe cy'ibanze, mu gihe ibipimo bya CT [computed tomography] bishobora kugaragara mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Ibintu biranga CT birimo impande zitandukanye z'impande hamwe na bilateral multilobar ground-glass opacification.
Uko indwara igenda irushaho gukomera, ni na ko habaho ubwigenge bwo mu mutwe, gusakuza no kwihuza.
Ubushakashatsi buhuriweho bwa PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, bugaragaza ko nubwo CT idasanzwe cyane, ariko ifite ibisubizo byinshi kurusha PCR, kuko ikubiyemo izindi ndwara ziterwa na nimoniya n'izindi ndwara.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirase cyatanze inama ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa nk'igikorwa cya mbere cyo gupima cyangwa gusuzuma COVID-19".
Igicuri cy'umubiri gikora imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, harimo IgM na IgG, mu rwego rw'igisubizo cy'umubiri ku cyorezo.
Ibizamini bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu, kumenya ubudahangarwa no gukurikirana abaturage nyuma yiminsi 7 cyangwa nyuma y'igihe runaka ibimenyetso bitangiye. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa na Laboratwari nkuru (CLT) cyangwa ibizamini bya Point of Care (POCT).
Ibizamini bizakorwa n'ibigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi bizaba bifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini byinshi byakozwe n'ububiko bwihariye mu gihe runaka, ariko kuboneka kwabyo bizaterwa n'igiciro cy'igicuruzwa cya buri buhinga.
Nubwo ibipimo byinshi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara, ibipimo by'amaraso y'ibanze ni byo bikunze gukoreshwa mu guhangana na CLT.
Kugira ngo haboneke ibimenyetso bya POCT, akenshi hakorwa isuzuma rimwe ry'amaraso binyuze mu gutobora uruhu.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, nta kuvanaho mbere yo gusuzuma. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatangaje amazina y'ibikoresho 29 byatanze amabwiriza ku kigo nk'uko bikenewe, bityo bikaba bishoboka ko byatanga ibizamini byabyo bya antibiyotike.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, FDA yemeje ikigo kimwe gusa cy'igerageza mu buryo bw'ibanze. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, EuroImmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitome Diagnostics byemerewe n'umuryango w'iburayi ku bikoresho byabo by'igerageza, bishobora gupima IgG na IgA antibodies mu maraso bitewe na virusi iri mu cyitegererezo.
Ubushobozi bw'ibizamini ni bwinshi ku buryo ibipimo amagana bishobora gupimwa mu masaha make, bityo bikaba byihuta inshuro nyinshi ugereranyije n'ibizamini bya PCR bisanzwe bya virusi ya RNA.
Ubusanzwe, imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara ishobora kuboneka mu minsi 14 nyuma yo kwandura. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta miti y'indwara igabanya ubukana bw'indwara y'ibicurane bwigeze buhabwa ubushobozi bwo gukoresha.
