Kugeza ku ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini byo gutwara abantu mu modoka byari byatangijwe mu mijyi minini.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzi, kuko hari hamaze kugaragara gusa ibipimo byiza.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwa laboratwari bwagaragaje ko nibura ibipimo 4,83,295 byasuzumwe kugeza ku cyumweru cya 12/2020 cy'ikirangaminsi no kugeza ku cyumweru cya 12/2020, kandi ibipimo 33,491 (6.9%) byemejwe ko bifite SARS-CoV-2.Abashakashatsi bo muri Israel Technion na Rambam Hospital batangije kandi bakoresha uburyo bwo gusuzuma ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, aho ibipimo byose byateranwaga hamwe, kandi bikagenzurwa gusa iyo ibipimo byateranwaga hamwe byagaragaye ko bifite umusaruro.Ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020, BI yafunguye ikigo cya kane cy'ubushakashatsi bw'imiterere y'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo byitwa "O-YAN" (mu gishinwa: cyangwa mu cyongereza "Gifire Fire") i Wuhan, gishobora gupima ibipimo birenga 10,000 mu minsi irenga 2000.
BGI yubatswe mu minsi 5 igenzurwa na Wang Jian washinze, kandi ibi byerekana ko iyo ubushobozi bwo gupima butatangira ku gihe, Hubei yari kubona abarwayi 47% kandi ikoreshwa ry'igiciro cyo gutunganya isuzuma ryikubye kabiri.
Laboratwari ya Wuhan yakurikiwe byihuse na Huo-Yan Laboratories mu mijyi 12 yose yo mu Bushinwa, harimo Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing na Shanghai.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, umusaruro w'ibanze w'ibipimo bya buri munsi wari 50,000. Igishushanyo mbonera cya Origami Essays, cyashyizwe ahagaragara, cyerekana ibipimo byinshi, gishobora gupima ibipimo bya COVID-19 ku barwayi 1122 bikoresheje ibizamini 93 gusa.
Kugeza muri Werurwe, ikibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibipimo bidakwiye byabaye imbogamizi mu igeragezwa ry'ibipimo byinshi mu Burayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
