Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki z'umuntu agamije gukuraho umukungugu, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe mu gihe runaka cy'umunsi bifasha mu kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'umusonga n'iseru, zikwirakwira mu gihe umuntu afashe intoki mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero, mu gihe batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso y'uruhu).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa ni: mbere na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, nyuma yo gusukura igituza cy'umwana cyangwa guhindura indimu, mbere yo konsa umwana, mbere yo kurya no guteka ibiryo na nyuma cyangwa mbere no gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Iyo amazi n'isabune bidahari, gukaraba intoki n'isabune birashoboka, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gukaraba intoki mu bihe bikurikira:
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe cyo guteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura amakanzu cyangwa se nyuma yo koza umwana mu cyumba cy'isuku.
Nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa guhekenya.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biryo by'amatungo cyangwa ku binure byayo.
Gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ingeso yo kugira isuku ijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa mbere yo kujya kwa muganga bigabanya cyangwa bikanagabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi ni ukuzitandukanya n'ibintu bishobora guteza indwara (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bintu bishobora guteza indwara) n'ibikoresho bishobora kwangiza cyangwa guteza indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakorera mu biribwa cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zitandura; gukumira indwara ziterwa n'iseru; kugabanya ubwandu bw'imyanya y'ubuhumekero;
Muri ibyo harimo kugabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bwahinduye imibereho y'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, butuma bagira uburebure buciriritse.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iz'igifu ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu guhindura imyitwarire nk'ukugeza intoki n'isabune.
Ibi bintu byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa kubera izi ndwara ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Ibiganiro bifasha gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, bikaba bisa n'ibikoresho by'amazi meza mu baturage batagira amikoro menshi.
Kugabanuka kwa 48% kw'ibyago byo kurwara igifu bishobora kuba biterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabuni. Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mu buryo bw'ubushake mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu miryango ku isi hose ni bwo buryo bwonyine bufite ingaruka nziza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda igifu n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (ARI).
Pneumonia, ari nayo ARI ikomeye, ni imwe mu mpamvu nyamukuru zitera urupfu rw'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abana bagera kuri 18,000 buri mwaka.
Abana bagera kuri miliyoni 35 bapfa buri mwaka bazize iseseme n'indwara y'ibihaha.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bwinshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'impfu ziterwa n'iseru n'icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye, bikagabanya kimwe cya kane cy'iziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ubusanzwe gukaraba intoki bijyanirana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'ingingo z'ibikorwa by'amazi, isuku n'isuku (wash).
Gukaraba intoki birinda indwara z'inkoko zandura zikwirakwira binyuze mu guhura n'abantu.
Ingaruka nke z'ukwo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rukonja kandi rukangirika.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera indwara z'uruhu nk'ukubika intoki, guturika kw'ibibyimba by'intoki, cyangwa indwara y'uruhu, cyane cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubwibone budafite icyo buvuga (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gusiramura, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura igituza cy'umwana (guhindura indimu), mbere yo konsa umwana, mbere yo kurya no guteka cyangwa mbere yo gukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe, igihe ukwiriye gukaraba intoki kugira ngo wirinde kwandura, harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa ikindi gikomere; nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa gukorora; nyuma yo gukora ku binure by'inyamaswa cyangwa gukorakora inyamaswa no gukorakora imyanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni ibintu bikunze kuba mu gihe gito.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ingo zigera kuri 38.7% zikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki ari 95% muri Arabiya Sawudite, hafi 77% muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, na 23% mu Bushinwa. Hari uburyo bwo guhindura imikorere ubu bugaragaza ko ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni byiyongera mu bihe bikomeye.
Muri Filipine, gahunda y'ubwisungane mu kwivuza ishyirwa mu bikorwa n'ishami ry'uburezi, ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo kwifashisha mu kuzamura ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Kwica udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni buri munsi, gukaraba amenyo n'isuku, ni bimwe mu bigize gahunda y'igihugu.
Byakorewe mu buryo bugaragara muri Indoneziya.
Gukura mikorobe ku ruhu byongerwa no gukoresha isabune cyangwa umuti urimo amazi.
Imikorere y'ibikoresho by'isabune n'ibikoresho by'isuku ni ugugabanya ubuziranenge bw'umusemburo no kongera uburyo bw'isuku.
Amazi yonyine ntabwo ahagije mu gusukura uruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine birimo ibikomoka ku butaka ntibishobora guhita bisama mu mazi.
Ariko rero, isuku ikorwa binyuze mu kuzana amazi mu buryo bukwiriye.
Kubera imiterere y'isubiramo, isabune ivanze n'amazi ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe zaturutse ku mikoreshereze y'igihe cyahise.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwakozwe ku mikorobe zimuka mu isabune ifunze, bwagaragaje ko iyo mikorobe zishwe n'umwotsi, zitagomba kwimuka.
CDC iracyatanga inama igira iti "Gukoresha isabune y'amazi idakora ku ntoki ni byiza".
Amasabune acuruza imiti yica udukoko yarushijeho gukundwa n'abantu benshi.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya na kimwe cyerekana ko imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yica udukoko ikoreshwa mu kurwanya udukoko dukomoka ku bundi bwoko.
Icyakora, amasabune ya antibiyotike aba arimo ibintu bisanzwe bya antibiyotike nka trichlosan, ifite urutonde rwagutse rw'indwara z'ibice by'umubiri.
Ku bw'ibyo, nubwo nta miti yo kurwanya imihangayiko ya antibiyotike yatoranyijwe mu myambaro yica udukoko, ishobora kuba idakora neza nk'uko byavuzwe.
Usibye kuba ari surfactant na agent irinda uruhu, ibintu byakozwe mu buryo buhanitse nka pH regulator bishobora kuba arimo aside (acetic acid ascorbic acid, lactic acid), benzoic acid ikora ku ndwara n'ibindi bikoresho byo kuvura uruhu (ibishyimbo, vitamini, menthol, ibimera). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health bwerekanye ko isabune isanzwe igira ingaruka nziza mu kuvura no kwirinda udukoko nk'uko bimeze ku isabune z'ubucuruzi za trichlosacyanide.
Amazi ashyushye meza yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo ahagije mu kwica mikorobe.
Imirambo ikura cyane iyo umuntu afite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 C.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye aruta cyane amazi akonje y'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta y'ibyatsi n'udukoko twanduye mu ntoki.
Nyamara, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babibona, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko amazi ashyushye adashobora kugabanya mikorobe ku biganza.
Umwandazi w'amaboko cyangwa umuti wica udukoko two mu biganza ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udafite amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki bitagira amazi (bizwi kandi nka rubs z'intoki zishingiye ku nzoga, rubs z'intoki z'ubuhumekero cyangwa se sanitizer z'intoki) byatangiye gukundwa.
Byinshi muri byo biba biri mu buryo bwa gel hamwe na karubomeri (polymeri ya acrylic acid) hamwe na isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol hamwe na formulations hamwe na agensi yo gutwika, cyangwa mu buryo bw'amazi y'umwotsi nka glycerine, cyangwa mu buryo bw'ifumba yoroshye gukoresha kandi igabanya ingaruka zo kumira za alcohol.
Umuvuduko muto wa Hydrogene-peroxide utuma imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara. Alcohol iri hagati ya 60 na 90% mu bikoresho byo gusukura intoki ni umuti wica udukoko.
Alcohol rub yica mikorobe z'ibiyobyabwenge, mikorobe zidakira imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu n'izindi mikorobe (zirimo HIV, Herpes, RSV, Rhinovirus, Vaccine, Influenza na Hepatitis) n'ibiheri
Alcohol rub sanitizer igizwe na 70% by'inzoga kandi yica 99,97% by'indwara ku ntoki (igabanuka rya 3,5 logs ringana na 35 decibels) mu masegonda 30 nyuma yo kuyishyiraho, na 99,99% na 99,99% (igabanuka rya 4 na 5 logs) nyuma y'umunota umwe ushyiriweho.
Amavuta yo gusukura intoki akoreshwa ku nzoga nta ngaruka na nkeya agira ku mikorobe nka Norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari nayo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'urwungano rw'amaraso. Gukoresha imiti yo gusukura intoki myinshi cyangwa rubine y'inzoga ni byiza kugira ngo ukarabe intoki neza.
Gukaraba intoki zombi imbere n'inyuma ndetse n'ibice byo hagati by'intoki zose kugeza amazi, isosi cyangwa gel byumye mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30.
Nanone, jya ukaraba intoki, ukarabe n'ibiganza byombi. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda, gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki mu gihe zanduye.
Imikoreshereze y'ibi bikoresho iri kwiyongera kubera uburyo bworoshye bwo kubikoresha no kwica mikorobe vuba, ariko ntibikwiye kuba uburyo bwo gusimbuza gukaraba intoki neza mu gihe nta sabune n'amazi bihari.
Kubera ko gukoresha kenshi imiti yo guhanagura uruhu ikoreshwa n'inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rukonja, jya uyikoresha ukoresheje imiti yo guhanagura uruhu n'imiti yo guhumura.
Iyi foromo ishobora kugabanya cyangwa se ikuraho ingaruka zo kumena inzoga, ikongeraho glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byoroshya uruhu.
Mu igeragezwa mu buvuzi, imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo imyuka itera imyuka ihumanya umubiri, yatuma uruhu rudakonja cyane kandi rukagira ubushyuhe budahagije ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura imiti igabanya ubukana.
Indwara z'uruhu zituruka ku mikoranire n'indwara z'uruhu, indwara y'igifu cyangwa indwara y'umuvuduko ukabije w'inzoga cyangwa ibintu biboneka mu myenda y'intoki.
Kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ufite ikibazo cyo kurwara uruhu, byateje ikibazo cyo kutagira ubushake bwo kurwara uruhu ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'amazi.
Nubwo ari ingirakamaro, ibikoresho bitanga amazi ntibikora isuku y'intoki ku bintu by'ibinyabuzima, ahubwo biyica gusa.
Ni yo mpamvu imiti yo guhanagura intoki idakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara kuko indwara ziguma ku ntoki.
Imikorere y'imiti yo guhanagura intoki idafite inzoga ishingiye cyane ku bintu byinshi hamwe n'uburyo ikoreshwamo kandi mu mateka yarushije cyane inzoga n'inzoga z'inzoga.
Vuba aha, uburyo bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwagaragaje ibikorwa bya antibiyotike bihoraho kandi bibitswe, bitandukanye na alukoro, aho byagaragaye ko ingufu zigabanuka nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'ibisubizo bibi by'uruhu bigenda byiyongera.
Abantu benshi bo mu cyiciro cy'abakennye ntibashobora kubona isabune, bakoresha imyanda n'ibitaka.
Ivu n'ivu bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine ariko zikaba zidafite ingaruka nziza nk'isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa imyanda byanduye, bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanuka.
