Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ubuziranenge n'ubuzima mu gucunga ibyago byo kwirinda Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gutegeka neza ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'aho akazi gakorerwa n'imiterere yako, bitewe n'isoko y'ubwandu, uburemere bw'uburwayi mu baturage n'ibyago by'umukozi wese ushobora kuba afite COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gashobora guteza ubwandu buke ni akazi kabamo guhura n'abantu n'abandi bakozi ku buryo buciriritse, aho inama z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zirimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka no gusukura no guhumeka ahantu hakorerwa imirimo buri gihe.
Imirimo y'ibyago byo kwandura mu buryo bworoheje ikubiyemo imirimo isaba guhura cyane cyangwa kwegera abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bahura n'abaturage muri rusange, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo hari abaturage benshi ndetse no mu bigo by'ubucuruzi binini.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, kugenzura ibyago by'iki cyiciro birimo gukoresha amavuta meza cyane, gukoresha udukingirizo two mu maso no kugira ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe umuntu ahanganye na COVID-19.
OSHO ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu marembo bahuye n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 nk'abashobora kwandura cyane, mu gihe uwo mukozi akora ibikorwa bitanga aerosol cyangwa akorakoranya cyangwa agakora ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, bigatuma habaho ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Ibigo by'ubugenzuzi bw'ibyago by'abo bakozi birimo ibyuma by'ubwubatsi nk'ibyumba by'umwuka uhumanya ibipimo bibi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye uwo murimo.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaza ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kubera ko bakeneye kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera gutinya ubwandu.
Mu buryo bw'ibikoresho bisabwa n'uburyo bwo kubikuraho, ibicuruzwa bishobora guhinduka (nk'ibicuruzwa bigurwa igihe abantu badafite umurindi, cyangwa kugura binyuze mu bikorwa byo gutanga cyangwa gutwara ibintu).
Amaherezo, ibicuruzwa bishobora guhungabana biturutse mu turere tuzwiho kuba twugarijwe cyane na COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibyago bijyanye n'akazi n'aho imirimo ikorerwa bivuga ku bintu bitandukanye, harimo isoko y'ubwandu, ibyago bituruka mu ngo n'imibanire y'abantu n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye, nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'igihe kirekire.
Bazafata ingamba zo guhangana n'ibyo byago, kandi bagaragaze gahunda z'ibikoresho bya leta ku bibazo bishobora kuvuka.
Gutegura no gutegura ibisubizo by'indwara zandura bishobora gukurikiza amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara zidakira, gukomeza imikorere y'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bintu mu ikoranabuhanga.
Uburemere bw'indwara bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buba.
Gushyiraho ingengabihe y'imiyoborere y'ibyago bikoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi, ni uburyo bwo gushyira hamwe ibipimo by'ingaruka z'imiyoborere y'ibyago.
Aho ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho burundu, ingamba nziza cyane ni ingamba z'ubwubatsi, hanyuma ingamba z'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Ingufu z'ubwubatsi zirimo gutandukanya abakozi n'ibibi bijyanye n'akazi aho gushingira ku myitwarire y'umukozi kandi bishobora kuba uburyo bworoshye bwo kubishyira mu bikorwa.
Gucunga ubuyobozi ni uguhindura politiki cyangwa imikorere y'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa muntu (PPE) ntibikora neza nk'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda indwara zimwe na zimwe.
