B'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ((ACE2) ni enzymes ifata ku gice cy'inyuma cy'ingirabuzimafatizo (cells sheath) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ikumira ibikorwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) irebana na yo, igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II kandi igatuma ingano ya Ang ((1-7) yiyongera, bityo ikaba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme mu bantu, akenshi bwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni metaloenzyme irimo zinc, iba ku gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal colectrain renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu, ikora ku mibiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Uru rugingo rw'inyongera rwa ACE2 rusimburwa n'urundi rugingo rw'amaraso rwitwa shades, maze poroteyine zishobora gukama zigasohoka mu maraso, amaherezo zikarenga mu cyuma.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo hafi ya zose: mu maraso, mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero bw'ubwoko bwa II, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu mara mato, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu mitsi n'imitsi, no mu nsoro z'umubiri mu ngingo nyinshi.
ACE2 mRNA kandi iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, mu gice cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cyitwa brainstem.
Inshingano y'ibanze ya ACE2 ni uguhangana na ACE.
ACE ituma umusemburo wa angiotensin I ujya mu musemburo wa angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo ihindura amino acide ya carboxyl-terminal ikayivamo angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihindura hydrolyzed mu bwoko bwa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
[des-Arg9]-Bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin, hamwe n'izindi peptides nyinshi, ACE2 ishobora gusenyuka.
ACE2 itegeka kandi uburyo bwo gutwara amino acide mu buryo butari bwo SLC6A19 kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya HATANOP.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine itera uturemangingo, ikora nk'ahantu h'ibanze habonekera virusi zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza inzego za enzymatic za ACE2 ku gice cy'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo na poroteyine ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ya S1 bigira ingaruka kuri endocytosis, kandi kwimurwa kwa virusi na enzymes byombi bibaho muri endosomes iri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Uburyo bwo kwinjira busaba kandi ko poroteyine S ya TMPRSS2 ya serine y'umwakiranyi ikora, ubu bufasha mu kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, inzego nyinshi z'ubucuruzi n'izigenga zasabye ko hakomeza gukoresha imiti isanzwe ya ACE inhibitor na ARB.
Isesengura ryagaragaye ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryanditseho kandi rivuga ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byahitanye amahirwe ya 34% yo kugabanuka kwa pneumonia ugereranyije n'abatabifite".
Byongeye kandi, abarwayi bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara amapfupfa, cyane cyane abafite ibibazo byo kurwara umutima no kurwara indwara y'igicuri, igihe bavurwaga n'imiti igabanya ingufu za ACE, byagabanyije ibyago byo kurwara.
Nubwo ingaruka za ACE inhibitors zari nke ugereranyije n'ibyago byose byo kurwara amapfa, gukoresha ACE byari bifite aho bihuriye no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na amapfa.
Umuntu usanzwe witwa ACE 2 (rhACE2) ni uburyo bushya bwo kuvura ibikomere by'ibihaha, kandi byagaragaye ko bwahinduye imikorere y'amaraso n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu bana b'ingurube bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba.
Mu bantu, igice cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 ni amasaha agera ku 10 mu gihe ingaruka zitangira mu minota 30 mu gihe igihe cy'ingaruka ari amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu batemera imiti ya RAS (Renin-angiotensin system inhibitors) cyangwa indwara ziterwa no kudahuza mu buryo bugaragara. RhACE2 yaterwa mu miti y'ubuvuzi yagenzuwe mu kwivuza indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Porogaramu za b-COVID-19 ni porogaramu za mudasobwa zigendanwa, zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha abantu guhura mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya umuntu wahuye n'umuntu wanduye ("contact").
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zashyizweho kandi zasabwe hamwe n'ubufasha bwemewe na leta mu ntara zimwe na zimwe n'uturere.
Hashyizweho uburyo bwinshi bwo gukora porogaramu zo gushakisha abakundana.
Impungenge ku byerekeye ubuzima bwite, by'umwihariko mu buryo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari, byagaragajwe.
Mu bintu bidakenewe cyane harimo gukoresha ikimenyetso cya Bluetooth mu kwandikisha amakuru y'umunyamuryango kuri telefoni ye.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku mugaragaro ko izo porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth zizashyirwamo ubushobozi bwo gushyigikira mu buryo butaziguye mu buryo bw'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, Leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu yo kureba niba abaturage barigeze guhura n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Iyi porogaramu ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa, muri Singapore ikoreshwa na porogaramu yitwa TREAS TOGETHER.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo mu karere, kandi yatanzwe nk'isoko ryuguruye kandi izatangwa na guverinoma.Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ishingiye kuri BlueTooth "Stop Corona" yo kuvugana n'abantu bashobora kwandura no guhita bitabira abayobozi b'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza tariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Guverinoma yatangaje ku ya 12 Mata 2020 ko porogaramu iri mu byiciro byiterambere kandi ko izaboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi irateganywa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("Stop COVID").
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande byombi birimo gutekereza kuri porogaramu zishingiye kuri Trace Together na Blue Tooth Protocol ya Singapore. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gushyiraho porogaramu yo guhanga imiterere y'isi igamije gufasha abarwayi banduye COVID-19 baba i Moscou, kugira ngo birinde kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere ishingiye kuri APR, harimo ko iyo APR ikoreshejwe mu bantu bake cyane, ikora nabi kandi ko nta bushobozi buhagije bwo gukora neza.
Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'ibigo bishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus mu bubiko bwayo bwa porogaramu, bikumira gusa ibigo "byemewe" cyangwa byemewe.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikira ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge zikomeye ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa byinshi byo kugenzura hakoreshejwe porogaramu za Coronavirus, cyane cyane niba ibikorwa by'ibanze byakozwe mu kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus bishobora kwangirika.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe agera ku 100 yasabye ko ibyo bikorwa by'ubugenzuzi bihagarikwa.
