Gukurikirana mu buryo bwa digitale bigomba kwirinda ivangura rikomeye no kwirengagizwa;
Gushyira hamwe amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba gusobanurwa n'amategeko;
uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo kurinda no guhangana n'ibikorwa bibi;
Uruhare rw'abafite aho babogamiye bose, harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'imiryango ititabwaho, rurakenewe. Urutonde rw'ibikoresho byakozwe na Reporters Without Borders (RSF) na German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na rwo rwaratanzwe.
Gahunda iteganyijwe na Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cyo gukuraho burundu uburyo bwo gukurikirana ibikoresho byabo mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga iyo bikenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bikoresha uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari aho akorera aho gukoresha porogaramu, aho gusaba ko hakoreshwa porogaramu, bityo ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikirana bukagenda bugabanuka.
Mu gihugu cya Israel, uburyo bwo gukurikirana hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga bwemewe.
