Mu gihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo, ikoranabuhanga ridakoreshejwe mu ikoranabuhanga ryatumye abantu bashobora guhura n'abandi.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakoresheje amakuru atandukanye yo gukurikirana, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga hamwe namakuru y'ibicuruzwa by'ikarita, kandi ikomatanya kugirango abantu bashobora kwandura batange imenyesha binyuze mu butumwa bwanditse.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo abantu bamenye aho bashobora guhurira, leta yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, nyuma y'ihindagurika rya MERS muri icyo gihugu, bitewe n'impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko y'ibanga ry'amakuru, hari ikintu cyemewe.
Ibi birashoboka binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website, ibihugu byinshi birimo n'u Budage byatangiye gutekereza uburyo bwo gushyira hamwe no kurinda ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta bisobanuro byatanzwe.
Ibanga - Gukora contact tracing bifite umutekano ni igitekerezo cyashyizweho neza, gifite ibitabo byubushakashatsi byatangiye nibura mu 2013. Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi yakoraga ku buryo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugirango umukozi agere hafi ya telefoni ye igendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza ibintu, ufite uburyo bwigenga kandi butari bumwe, kandi nta protocole imwe. Porotokolo zitari zimwe zirimo ubuzima bwite butari bumwe - Kugaragaza kwegereza (DP-PPT/DP-3T), nimero z'imishyikirano z'igihe gito (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), protocole z'ibanga na sisitemu yo gukurikirana abakora kuri telefoni zigendanwa (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ayo mabwiriza, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye nta na rimwe ava ku gikoresho kandi byose biba biri ku gikoresho gihuza.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora SafePath, urubuga rwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya cyangwa gukoresha ahantu cyangwa inzira z'umuhanda kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu igazeti y'ibanze "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" yasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikindi gikorwa gisa n'icyo ni SafeTrace, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga ritanga amakuru y'ibanga cyakozwe na Enigma MPC, cyashinzwe mu kigo cya MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bya mudasobwa bifite umutekano, bituma umukoresha asangira amakuru y'ahantu ahishe n'andi makuru y'ubuzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi, nta guhungabanya ubuzima bwite bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Inteko y'Isi Yose ya TCN yashinzwe n'amatsinda yari ahuriye hamwe agendera ku buryo bumwe kandi ahanini buhuriweho n'amabwiriza agamije kugabanya ihurizo, gukurikirana no kongerera ubushobozi za porogaramu zitanga amakuru, ari nabyo by'ingenzi mu bikorwa byo kuyakira cyane.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, Guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize ku isoko rya BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu yayo yemewe na guverinoma.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imbuga za Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakora amakuru hashingiwe ku buryo bumwe bwa Bluetooth ikoranabuhanga rito ry'ingufu na cryptography y'ibanga, bavuga ko bizakomeza ubuzima bwite.
Yongeyeho kandi ko hari n'ibimenyetso by'ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa muri iyi gahunda.
Apple na Google bavuga ko iyi gahunda ishobora gukorwa mu byiciro bitatu:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho bifasha guverinoma guharanira ibanga rya leta - Kurinda porogaramu zo gukurikirana Coronavirus.
Kwishyira hamwe kw'izi mikorere mu buryo butaziguye muri iOS, Android, Google na Apple biteganyijwe ko bizajya bifasha mu gukemura ibibazo by'ubwiteganyirize buhoraho binyuze mu gutanga sisitemu ya mbere binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere no kongera gukemura ikibazo nyuma yo kwirinda ibyago.
Gushyiraho imiti (b) (Icyitwa kandi gusubizaho imiti, kongera gusubizaho, gusubizaho cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuvura) ni ugukoresha umuti wemewe ku burwayi bumwe cyangwa ubundi mu kuvura ubundi burwayi.
Ni ubushakashatsi bw'ubwoko bumwe mu bushakashatsi bwa siyansi bukorwa muri iki gihe mu rwego rwo gukora imiti idahungabanya indwara ya COVID-19.
Indwara z'ibicurane mu mubiri ziterwa n'urukingo n'ubuvuzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine 66 zishobora gukurwaho, buri imwe ifite ahantu henshi hahuza.
Gusuzuma ahantu nk'aho ho guhuza bituma habaho uburyo bwiza bwo gukora imiti ya virusi ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya poroteyine za COVID-19.
Poroteyine z'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira ni za proteyine nka Papane, RNA-dependent RNA polymerases, helicases, S proteins, na ADP ribophosphateases.
