Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara yandura iterwa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe (SARS-CoV-2).
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe ni umuriro, inkorora n'ubuhumekero buke.
Ibindi bimenyetso bishobora kuba umunaniro, kubabara mu musatsi, iseseme, kubabara mu muhogo, guhumeka nabi no kuribwa n'igifu.
Ubusanzwe, ibimenyetso by'iki cyorezo bitangira kugaragara nyuma y'iminsi itanu, ariko bishobora gutangira kugaragara nyuma y'iminsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi 14.
Abenshi mu barwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje, mu gihe hari abarwayi bagenda barushaho kuremba bigatuma barwara ibicurane by'imyanya y'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Mata 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi barenga miliyoni 2.24 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, mu gihe abamaze gupfa ari 153.000.
Abantu barenga 568,000 bamaze gukira iyi ndwara, ikwirakwira mu bantu ahanini binyuze mu guhura n'abantu, akenshi binyuze mu gukorora, guhekenya cyangwa gusohora umunwa.
Iyo umuntu ahumetse, ayo mazi asohoka mu mubiri, agakoroka ku butaka cyangwa ku butaka, bityo ntiyatwara indwara mu birometero byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kwandura iyo bakomeje gukora ku bintu byanduye, bakoresheje amaso, amazuru n'umunwa.
Iyi virusi ishobora kubaho ku kintu icyo ari cyo cyose mu gihe cy'amasaha 72.
Ni indwara yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere y'igiteranyo cy'indwara, ariko ishobora no gukwirakwira mu bihe by'imbere y'igiteranyo cy'indwara n'inyuma y'igiteranyo cy'indwara. Ikoranabuhanga ryo gupima indwara mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga (rRT-PCR) ni uburyo bwo gupima indwara.
Abashakashatsi bagaragaje ko abantu bakekwaho kwandura iyi virus n'ababafasha, basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Abaturage batanga inama zitandukanye ku bijyanye no kwambara udupfukamunwa, bamwe mu bayobozi barwanya kwambara udupfukamunwa, abandi baracyatangaza, abandi baracyemeza ko ari ngombwa.
Kugeza ubu nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwihariye rwa COVID-19 ruriho.
Ibihugu byinshi byo mu turere dutandatu twa OMS byatangaje ko hari ubwandu bw'indwara.
Abarwayi banduye virusi rimwe na rimwe ntibagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa bakagira ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane, urugero nk'umuriro, inkorora, umunaniro no guhumeka nabi.
Mu bimenyetso by'ihungabana harimo guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa gukomera, kugira iseseme, kugenda nabi no kugira ubururu mu maso no ku munwa, ibi bimenyetso bikagirwa inama yo kujya kwa muganga ako kanya.
Ibimenyetso byoroheje bishobora kuba ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nko guhumeka, guhekenya mu mazuru cyangwa kuribwa mu muhogo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'indwara y'igifu mu rugero ruciriritse, nko kugira iseseme, gusubiranamo no gucibwamwo.
Abarwayi bamwe na bamwe bo mu Bushinwa bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya mbere by'ububabare mu gatuza no kudahuma kw'umutima.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje ko indwara yabo yateye imbere, bituma barwara amapfupfa, bagapfa ndetse bagapfa.
Icyo gihe cyitwa igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro.
Ubusanzwe igihe cyo kubumbatira COVID-19 ni iminsi itanu kugeza kuri itandatu, ariko hari n'abashobora kumara iminsi ibiri kugeza kuri 14.
97.5% by'abarwayi bagaragaje ibimenyetso mu minsi 11.5 nyuma yo kwandura. Raporo zigaragaza ko abanduye bose batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Uruhare rw'abo batwara indwara badafite ibimenyetso mu kwanduzanya ntiruzwi neza, ariko hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze bigaragaza ko bagira uruhare mu gukwirakwiza iyi ndwara.
Umubare w'abarwayi batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu ntiwaramenyekanye kandi ubushakashatsi burakomeje, kandi abagera kuri 20% mu barwayi bemejwe n'ikigo cyo muri Koreya gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (KCDC) bavuga ko batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu kugeza igihe bari mu bitaro.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'Ubushinwa yatangiye gushyira abarwayi batagira ibimenyetso mu barwayi ba buri munsi guhera ku ya 1 Mata; mu barwayi 166 banduye bagaragaye uwo munsi, 130 (78%) nta bimenyetso bari bafite igihe bagenzurwaga.
