Iyo umuntu ahangayikishijwe no kwandura binyuze mu myanda, ibyago byo kwandura byibarwa ko ari bike, kandi abantu bafite ibimenyetso ni bo bakunze kwandura virusi cyane.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitaramenyekana neza uko iyi ndwara yandura, umuntu umwe ashobora kwandura abantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
Mu by'ukuri, iyi virusi yagaragaye ku ikarito y'impapuro mu gihe cy'umunsi umwe, ku bikoresho bya plastiki n'ibyuma (AISI 304) mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu, naho ku bikoresho bifite umuringa ku kigero cya 99%, mu gihe cy'amasaha ane.
Ariko kandi, biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe bwo mu kirere kandi bigahinduka.
Amasabune n'imiti ikoreshwa mu gusukura imyanda ishobora gukoreshwa neza mu kurwanya iyi virusi, kuko imyenda ikoreshwa mu gusukura imyanda ituma iyo virusi idakora, ikayihuma kandi ikayigobotora ku ruhu no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
Ibindi bikoresho, nk'imiti yitwa benzakonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate (ubundi buryo bwo kuvura indwara mu kubaga) ntibikora cyane. Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe muri Hong Kong, ibipimo by'amaraso byafashwe nyuma y'iminsi ibiri umuntu yinjiye ibitaro.
Mu barwayi batanu muri batandatu, icyiciro cya mbere cyerekanye umubare munini w'indwara, naho icyiciro cya gatandatu cyerekanye umubare munini w'indwara ku munsi ukurikiyeho.
SIVERS Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya ya coronavirusi ifite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero. Yatangiye gutandukanywa n'abarwayi batatu barwaye ibicurane by'ubuhumekero mu kigo cy'indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero kiri i Wuhan.
Imiterere yose y'iyi virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 igaragara mu mikoranire yayo na koronavirusi zo mu rwego rwa kamere.
Hasi y'umubiri w'umuntu, iyi virusi yica isabune yo mu rugo ikora igifu cyayo cy'ubwirinzi. Inkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane ibihaha, kuko virusi igera ku ngirabuzimafatizo binyuze kuri angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2), iboneka cyane mu zindi ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Iyi virusi ikoresha igipimo cy'umusemburo wa glycoprotein wihariye witwa 'spike' kugira ngo ifatanye na ACE2 maze yinjire mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'inkomoko.
Mu baturage bo mu Bushinwa, 12% by'abarwayi barwariye mu bitaro bya Wuhan bagaragaweho kugira umutima utera cyane kandi akenshi ugaragara mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
