Ibitandukaniro by'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bitewe n'igitsina, kuba abagore batanywa itabi cyane no kuba abagabo barwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso ukabije mu myaka y'amavuko ugereranyije n'abagore, byose bishobora kuba ari byo bituma abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo, naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiyari ifite amakuru y'itandukaniro ry'ibitsina mu bantu banduye COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara zituruka ku mikorobe, nka Ebola, HIV, ibicurane na SARS, zigira ingaruka ku bagabo n'abagore mu buryo butandukanye.
Abakozi benshi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko izina ry'ubuvuzi ry'iyi ndwara rizaba "COVID-19".
Tendrose Edhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi wa OMS, yavuze ko CO isobanura Coronavirus, VI isobanura Virusi, D isobanura Indwara, kandi 19 ni umwaka icyorezo cyatangiriye kugaragara: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iri zina ryatanzwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwerekeza ku karere runaka (urugero, Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa, cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe inama mpuzamahanga ku byerekeye amazina, kandi hagamijwe kwirinda gutesha agaciro umuntu uwo ari we wese. Iyi virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Mu itangazamakuru rya WHO, hakoreshwa amagambo "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi iteza COVID-19" uretse "virusi ya COVID-19".
Iyo ndwara na virusi byombi bikunze kwitwa "coronavirus".
Igihe iki cyorezo cyatangiraga mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byombi byitwaga "Coronavirus" na "Wuhan Coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yateye inkunga 2019-nCoV na 2019-nCoV Acute Respiratory Disease nk'amazina y'agateganyo kuri virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha izina ry'ahantu mu mazina y'indwara n'ubwandu.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu buryo bw'ibanze, hari abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga bacapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupira two mu mazuru n'ibice by'imashini zitanga umwuka.
Urugero, igihe ivuriro ryo mu Butaliyani ryari rikeneye cyane umugozi wo guhumeka kandi abaguzi batabashije kuwutanga ku gihe, ikigo cy'aho cyatangiye gukora imashini z'ubwubatsi zinyuranye z'ibanze, maze zandikaho udupfukamunwa 100 mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, amakuru atari yo, ibinyoma n'ibinyoma ku nkomoko, ubukana, uburyo bwo kuvura n'ibindi by'iki cyorezo byatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti.
Abantu basanze bashobora gukwirakwiza iyi virusi mu bindi bikoko.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwananiwe kubona ibimenyetso byerekana ko virusi ishobora kugaragara mu ngurube, ibitunguru n'inkoko.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvurwa iyi ndwara.
Ubu bushakashatsi ku ruhando mpuzamahanga ku rukingo n'umuti wa COVID-19 burakomeje.
Muri Werurwe, OMS yatangije "igerageza ry'ubwiyunge" ryo gusuzuma ingaruka z'imiti ine ya virusi iriho ubu ikora neza cyane.
Nubwo nta rukingo ruhari, ibigo bitandukanye biri gukora cyane 'abakandida b'urukingo'.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere kuri SARS-CoV-2 burakoreshwa, kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bwavumbuwe.
Icya mbere, intego y'abashakashatsi ni ugukora urukingo rwa virusi yose.
Igikorwa cyo gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite imbaraga cyangwa yapfuye, ni ugutera indwara nshya ifitanye isano na COVID-19 mu buryo bwihuse bw'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda.
Uburyo bwa kabiri ni inkingo z'udutsiko duto, zigamije gukora inkingo zituma ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri buhinduka bugahura n'udutsiko duto tw'agakoko.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi gucika ku myakura y'imyakura ikoreshwa na ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubwo gukoresha urukingo rwa nucleic acid (inkingo za DNA cyangwa RNA, ikoranabuhanga rishya mu gukora inkingo).
Muri izo ngamba eshatu, icyiciro icyo ari cyo cyose cy'urukingo rw'igerageza kigomba kugeragezwa ku bw'umutekano n'imikorere. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, urukingo rwatangiye igeragezwa mu buvuzi mu mujyi wa Seattle, rufite abitangiye kurwitaho bane.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'ibinyabuzima itariho ibyago, yakuwe muri virusi itera iyi ndwara. Gushyiraho uburyo bwo kurinda budafite abasirikare b'umubiri byagiye bivugwa ko ari imbogamizi mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko biravuguruzanya.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, raporo igaragaza ko hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byakozwe byasuzumaga uburyo bwo kuvura malaria bwamaze kwemerwa, harimo n'ibyigwa bine byakozwe kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bw'Abashinwa burimo imiti ikoreshwa mu buryo bwinshi, harimo icyenda mu igerageza rya III rya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi nk'uko byavuzwe mu mpera za Mata.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe muri raporo yo muri Mata 2020, hari isesengura ry'imikorere y'imiti n'imiti ya COVID-19 iri gukorwa. Hari imiti myinshi ya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, irimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Rytopinavir na Interferon beta hamwe na Lopinavir/Rytopinavir.
Nk'uko byavuzwe muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo byerekana ko Remdesivir igira ingaruka.
Abarwayi bavurwa na Remdesivir bagaragaje ko hari icyiza cyabaye.
Icyiciro cya gatatu cy'igeragezwa mu buvuzi muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshwaga mu kuvura malaria mbere, yakorewe ubushakashatsi mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, igatanga umusaruro w'ibanze.
Ariko kandi, ibyo byigisho bisaba ko abantu bose babigenzura.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'Ubushinwa batanze inama yo gukoresha chloroquine.
Icyakora, ikigo cyo muri Wuhan gishinzwe Virology cyatangaje ko ku munsi umuntu agomba guhabwa garama imwe y'umuti, ariko kivuga ko kuwufata kabiri ari akaga kandi ko ushobora kumuhitana.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse rwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine, hashingiwe ku bwenge bw'abaganga bavura abarwayi bafite COVID-19. Igitabo cy'ibanze cy'icya karindwi cy'ubushinwa nacyo kirimo interferon, raibavirine cyangwa umiphenovir yo gukoresha mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze avuga ko dosiye nini ya ribavirini ikenewe mu gupima SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe cyo kuyigerageza.
Nitasoxanide irasabwa mu bindi bizamini nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo kugabanya ibipimo. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangiza poroteyine ya spike mu buryo bwa transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa cyane kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 igere ku bantu binyuze mu guhura na ACE-2 tekinike.
Ubushakashatsi kuri chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bufite ibibazo bikomeye byatumye umuryango w'abaganga utagera kuri ubwo buvuzi hatabayeho ubundi bushakashatsi. Ocellatmivir ntiyabujije SARS-CoV-2 mu igerageza kandi nta ruhare ruzwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibihe by'ibiza bya sitokine bishobora gutera ibibazo mu cyiciro gikurikiraho cya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Ibi bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere yo kurwanya cytoquin. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa nyuma y'ubushakashatsi buto.
Nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, mu Butaliyani haracyakorwa igerageza ry'icyiciro cya kabiri mu rwego rw'igihugu.
Iyo ibipimo bya seriyamu bya ferritin bihujwe n'ibizamini by'amaraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ibiza bya sitokine, bishobora gutuma habaho kurwanya ibyago by'ibyorezo by'indwara z'umwijima, bikaba byaratangiye kwiba abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye.
Mu 2017, interleukin-6 neurotransmitter antagonist yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere yo kuvura indwara y'ubwonko ituma sitokine zidakira steroid zituma zitanga sitokine zitagira icyo zitwara zitwa CAR T cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya ihamye, itegekanywa neza, igaragaza ko tosilisizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Ubushakashatsi burakomeje ku buryo bwo gutera urukingo butari urukingo bwo gutanga abasirikare b'umubiri basukuye kandi bifatanyije n'abasirikare b'umubiri b'abantu bakize COVID-19 mu bantu babikeneye.
Ubwo buryo bwakoreshejwe mu kurwanya SARS, ariko nta ngaruka nziza bwagize.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora, bushobora kuvura SARS-CoV-2 ikoresheje umuti wa 'antibody' utabikora.
Icyakora, hari ubundi buryo bushoboka, urugero nk'ubushobozi bwo kurwanya udukoko twitwa cytotoxicity n'utundi dukoko twitwa phagocytes.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi b'indwara z'umwijima, urugero nko gukoresha imyanya ndangagitsina y'umubiri umwe.
Ihingwa rya serumu z'imishongi, zirimo poroteyine z'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi zirimo no kurinda virusi, zishobora kwiyongera kugira ngo zigere ku isura yihuse.
Indwara ya koronavirusi, itsinda ry'indwara zihuriyeho cyane.
Li Wenliang, umuganga wo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, yanduye COVID-19 nyuma yo gukangurira abantu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, maze arapfa.
